-jet-pilots-attacking-behind-russian-lines-ds5vdtpbs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20Sunday%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20limited%20impact%20that%20Ukraine's%20outdated%20gear%20can%20have.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERussia%20has%20changed%20its%20aviation%20tactics%2C%20which%20is%20proving%20difficult%20for%20Ukraine%20in%20its%20offensive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Ukrainian%20pilot%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fukraine-helicopter-jet-pilots-attacking-behind-russian-lines-ds5vdtpbs%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20Sunday%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20his%20country's%20air%20force%20is%20so%20outclassed%20by%20Russia%20that%20it%20can%20%26quot%3Bdo%20nothing%20to%20them%20in%20the%20air.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pilot%2C%20identified%20only%20by%20his%20rank%20of%20major%20and%20his%20first%20name%20Maksym%2C%20told%20the%20publication%20on%20Saturday%20that%20his%20team%20has%20been%20struggling%20in%20its%20missions%20around%20Bakhmut%20against%20a%20far%20better-armed%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20his%20fellow%20airmen%20fly%20a%20Soviet-designed%20Mil%20Mi-8%20helicopter%2C%20a%20model%20which%20entered%20service%20in%20the%20late%201960s%20and%20is%20far%20less%20effective%20than%20Russia's%20modern%20helicopter%20fleet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20outmoded%20gear%2C%20they%20also%20have%20limited%20ammo.%20Maksym%20said%20his%20crew%20flies%20only%20one%20mission%20a%20day%20because%20they%20don't%20have%20enough%20rockets%20for%20more%20attacks.%20The%20problem%2C%20he%20said%2C%20extends%20from%20helicopters%20to%20fighter%20jets%2C%20where%20Ukraine%20has%20nothing%20to%20counter%20Russia's%20newest%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Russian%20jets%20are%20much%20better%20quality%20than%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20Maksym%20told%20The%20Times.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20comparing%20a%20Mercedes%20to%20a%20Lada.%26quot%3B%20A%20Lada%20is%20a%20Soviet-era%20car%20from%20Russia%2C%20which%20had%20a%20reputation%20for%20being%20cheap%2C%20bulky%2C%20and%20unreliable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Russians%20are%20flying%20a%20large%20number%20of%20advanced%20combat%20aircraft%2C%20including%20the%20Kamov%20Ka-52%20helicopter%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ka-52%20is%20mainly%20designed%20for%20fierce%20battle%2C%20while%20the%20Mil%20Mi-8%20Maksym%20has%20is%20designed%20for%20troop%20transportation%20rather%20than%20fighting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Russians%20understand%20we%20can%20do%20nothing%20to%20them%20in%20the%20air%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Maksym.%20He%20said%20that%20half%20of%20his%20unit%20had%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaksim's%20comments%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-aviation-helicopters-cause-headaches-for-ukraine-armored-assaults-counteroffensive-2023-6%3Finternational%3Dtrue%26r%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Ecame%20after%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Russia%20has%20changed%20the%20way%20it%20uses%20its%20aviation%20assets%20as%20Ukraine%20launches%20its%20counter-offensive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESenior%20Ukrainian%20military%20officials%20said%20recently%20they%20were%20concerned%20about%20Russia's%20%26quot%3Baviation%20and%20artillery%20superiority.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20used%20helicopters%20to%20blunt%20Ukraine's%20attempts%20to%20advance%20using%20armored%20troop%20vehicles%20on%20land%2C%20which%2C%20%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fd8fe8941-3703-433d-ac7a-dab9ba500481%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%227462c15d9fde6d627501723fd79e7122%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2240%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fd8fe8941-3703-433d-ac7a-dab9ba500481%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20top%20British%20air%20force%20general%2C%20Chief%20Marshal%20of%20British%20Air%20Staff%20Rich%20Knighton%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-air-force-largely-intact-has-operational-problems-in-ukraine-2023-7%3Finternational%3Dtrue%26r%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Etold%20a%20conference%20in%20London%20last%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Russia's%20air%20force%20%26quot%3Bremains%20largely%20intact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECiting%20British%20intelligence%2C%20Knighton%20said%20that%20Russia's%20air%20force%20had%20retained%2096%25%20of%20its%202%2C021%20fixed-wing%20aircraft%20and%2090%25%20of%20its%20899%20helicopters%2C%20with%20losses%20of%2086%20planes%20and%2090%20helicopters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnighton%20said%20neither%20Russia%20nor%20Ukraine%20had%20been%20able%20to%20gain%20air%20superiority%2C%20but%20that%20Ukraine%20was%20facing%20%26quot%3Ba%20massive%20challenge%20without%20air%20superiority%20and%20without%20being%20able%20to%20strike%20the%20adversary%20in%20the%20deep.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-pilot-says-air-force-outclassed-by-russian-jets-report-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689590914000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b4ffd1dcdf1100194c2260%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-pilot-says-air-force-outclassed-by-russian-jets-report-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Ukrainian%20pilot%20told%20The%20Sunday%20Times%20that%20Ukraine's%20aging%20aircraft%20confronting%20Russia's%20is%20be%20%26quot%3Blike%20a%20Lada%20going%20up%20against%20a%20Mercedes.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sankel%40businessinsider.com%20(Sophia%20Ankel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-pilot-says-air-force-outclassed-by-russian-jets-report-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7