Fworld-australia-66220494.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ajit%20Pawar%20Meets%20With%20Uncle%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20Second%20Meeting%20In%2024%20Hours%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20who%20along%20with%20several%20loyalist%20MLAs%20recently%20rebelled%20against%20his%20uncle%20Sharad%20Pawar%20to%20join%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20will%20today%20meet%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20chief%2C%20the%20second%20such%20meeting%20in%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20meeting%20Sharad%20Pawar%20yesterday%2C%20the%20rebel%20camp%20said%20that%20they%20have%20requested%20the%20senior%20leader%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20party%20isn't%20divided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSharad%20Pawar%20didn't%20reply%20to%20us%2C%20he%20just%20kept%20on%20listening%20to%20what%20we%20were%20saying%20and%20after%20meeting%20him%2C%20we%20are%20going%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20NCP's%20Praful%20Patel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20addressed%20the%20party%20workers%20later%20in%20the%20day%20and%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20will%20continue%20his%20%26quot%3Bprogressive%20politics%26quot%3B%20and%20never%20ally%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCP%20patriarch%2C%2082%2C%20has%20been%20a%20leading%20player%20in%20trying%20to%20unite%20various%20parties%20against%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCP%20split%20earlier%20this%20month%20when%20Ajit%20Pawar%20left%20the%20Opposition%20ranks%20and%20took%20oath%20as%20the%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar%2C%20who%20claims%20the%20support%20of%20more%20NCP%20MLAs%20than%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20also%20visited%20his%20uncle's%20home%20last%20week%20to%20meet%20with%20his%20aunt%20Pratibha%20Pawar%20-%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20wife%20-%20who%20had%20a%20surgery%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22