2%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fdara-singh-chauhan-formally-joins-bjp%2Farticleshow%2F101823772.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20was%20scared%20of%20flying%20and%20took%20a%20course%20to%20help%20me.%20Here%20are%206%20things%20every%20nervous%20passenger%20should%20know.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sophia%20flying%20with%20confidence%20british%20ai%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ad450694be880019f3600d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22856%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESenior%20News%20Reporter%20Sophia%20Ankel%20attended%20British%20Airways'%20Flying%20with%20Confidence%20course%20on%20July%209%2C%202023.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Ankel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20took%20British%20Airways'%20Flying%20with%20Confidence%20course%20to%20help%20me%20overcome%20my%20fear%20of%20flying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20course%2C%20run%20by%20a%20team%20of%20pilots%2C%20cabin%20crew%2C%20and%20psychiatrists%2C%20taught%20me%20some%20valuable%20lessons.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%C2%A0Here%20are%206%20things%20every%20nervous%20passenger%20should%20know%20before%20getting%20on%20a%20plane.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can%20remember%2C%20I%20have%20hated%20flying.%20Everything%20from%20take-off%20to%20turbulence%2C%20and%20landing%20can%20evoke%20feelings%20of%20sheer%20panic%20in%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20worried%20about%20flights%20days%20in%20advance%2C%20have%20had%20panic%20attacks%20mid-air%2C%20and%20have%20held%20many%20strangers'%20hands%20during%20turbulence.%20And%20I%20know%20I'm%20not%20alone%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fhealth%2Flots-of-americans-have-a-fear-of-flying-there-are-way-to-overcome-the-anxiety-disorder%2F2019%2F10%2F11%2Fd4746d84-d338-11e9-86ac-0f250cc91758_story.html%5C%22%3Eup%20to%2040%25%20of%20Americans%20have%20a%20form%20of%20aerophobia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20otherwise%20known%20as%20the%20fear%20of%20flying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20face%20my%20fears%20head-on%2C%20I%20recently%20attended%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britishairways.com%2Fen-gb%2Finformation%2Ftravel-assistance%2Fflying-with-confidence%5C%22%3EBritish%20Airways'%20Flying%20with%20Confidence%20course.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one-day%20course%2C%20located%20in%20the%20Sofitel%20Hotel%20by%20Heathrow%20Airport%20in%20London%2C%20is%20designed%20to%20give%20people%20the%20knowledge%20and%20techniques%20they%20need%20to%20overcome%20their%20fear%20of%20flying.%20It%20costs%20around%20%C2%A3385%20(%24502).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20begins%20with%20a%20technical%20session%20led%20by%20a%20team%20of%20pilots%20and%20cabin%20crew%20members%2C%20who%20talk%20me%20and%20around%20100%20other%20nervous%20flyers%20through%20everything%20from%20how%20an%20airplane%20is%20designed%20to%20what%20turbulence%20actually%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20lunch%2C%20a%20psychiatrist%20provides%20us%20with%20breathing%20exercises%20and%20other%20tools%20to%20help%20us%20manage%20our%20phobia.%20Then%2C%20we%20all%20boarded%20a%20British%20Airways%20flight%20and%20flew%20around%20Heathrow%20Airport%20for%20around%2045%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20was%20incredibly%20emotional%20as%20the%20camaraderie%20and%20support%20I%20received%20from%20absolute%20strangers%20that%20day%20was%20heart-warming.%20But%20most%20importantly%2C%20it%20also%20taught%20me%20many%20new%20things%2C%20ultimately%20helping%20me%20rationalize%20my%20fears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20things%20I%20learned%20that%20might%20help%20other%20nervous%20flyers%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20A%20loud%20engine%20is%20a%20healthy%20engine%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20often%20over-analyzed%20every%20sound%20a%20plane%20makes%2C%20especially%20during%20take-off%20and%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20British%20Airways%20pilot%20Steve%20Allright%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20Flying%20with%20Confidence%20course%2C%20told%20us%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bloud%20engine%20is%20a%20healthy%20engine%26quot%3B%20because%20it%20means%20that%20it's%20doing%20its%20job.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20our%20test%20flight%2C%20Allright%20talked%20us%20through%20every%20individual%20sound%20coming%20from%20the%20plane.%20This%20included%20a%20loud%20squeaking%20noise%20that%20you%20hear%20after%20the%20aircraft%20has%20backed%20out%20of%20the%20gate%20and%20is%20preparing%20for%20take-off%2C%20which%20Allright%20described%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bbarking%20dog%26quot%3B%20noise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20simply%20the%20sound%20of%20the%20aircraft's%20hydraulic%20power%20system%20working%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20encourage%20people%20to%20assume%20that%20everything%20is%20normal%20unless%20they%20are%20told%20otherwise%2C%26quot%3B%20Allright%20told%20us.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20Turbulence%20is%20uncomfortable%20but%20not%20dangerous%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20people%2C%20my%20least%20favorite%20sensation%20in%20the%20sky%20is%20turbulence.%20But%20while%20it%20may%20feel%20uncomfortable%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20the%20pilots%20assured%20us%20that%20it%20is%20not%20dangerous.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhat-is-turbulence-causes-dangerous-airplanes-flight%5C%22%3EBy%20definition%2C%20turbulent%20air%20happens%20everywhere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20from%20ground%20level%20to%20far%20above%20cruising%20altitude.%20It%20has%20two%20common%20causes%3A%20jet%20streams%20and%20weather.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20all%20of%20the%20pilots%20on%20the%20course%20said%20that%20turbulence%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20normal%20sensations%20of%20flying%20and%20that%20they%20will%20always%20try%20to%20find%20the%20most%20comfortable%20path%20to%20their%20destination%20without%20compromising%20safety.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20also%20shown%20maps%20given%20to%20pilots%20before%20a%20flight%20that%20outline%20exactly%20where%20the%20jet%20streams%20are%20located%2C%20and%20where%20bad%20weather%20is%20%E2%80%94%20should%20there%20be%20any.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAllright%20likened%20turbulence%20to%20a%20ship%20that%20rests%20on%20a%20body%20of%20water%20and%20moves%20up%20and%20down%20as%20the%20water%20changes.%20Just%20like%20a%20ship%2C%20a%20plane%20is%20also%20resting%20on%20a%20body%20of%20air%20and%20moves%20the%20way%20the%20air%20moves%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurbulence%20is%20also%20rarely%20the%20cause%20of%20any%20major%20airplane%20accident.%20Between%202009%20and%202021%2C%20there%20were%20only%20between%20five%20and%2018%20serious%20turbulence-related%20injuries%20per%20year%2C%20according%20to%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faa.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fturbulence%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%221baa32e78dba917df06f79be5307521e%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2240%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faa.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fturbulence%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22957%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22healthrow%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ad6b1f94be880019f365dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22718%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20British%20Airways%20ticket%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bfictitious%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20was%20actually%20just%20flying%20around%20Heathrow%20Airport%20for%2045%20minutes.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Ankel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20The%20plane's%20wing%20physically%20cannot%20snap%20off%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20crazy%20as%20this%20may%20sound%2C%20I%20used%20to%20have%20an%20irrational%20fear%20that%20a%20plane's%20wing%20could%20snap%20off%20during%20turbulence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20same%20way%20that%20pilots%20always%20prepare%20for%20the%20worst%20kind%20of%20turbulence%2C%20aircraft%20designers%20do%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20that%20every%20modern%20aircraft%20has%20been%20designed%20to%20withstand%20far%20in%20excess%20of%20the%20worst%20conditions%20that%20could%20ever%20be%20experienced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20the%20wings%20of%20a%20Boeing%20787.%20During%20testing%20they%20are%20strained%20to%20way%20beyond%20what%20they%20would%20ever%20experience%20even%20in%20the%20most%20severe%20turbulence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20did%20you%20know%20an%20aircraft%20only%20actually%20has%20one%20wing%20that%20is%20connected%20by%20the%20fuselage%20and%20therefore%20makes%20a%20plane%20more%20sturdy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20A%20plane%20can%20glide%20for%20up%20to%20100%20miles%20without%20any%20engines%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEngine%20failure%20is%20another%20fear%20among%20nervous%20flyers%2C%20but%20it%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20most%20rehearsed%20and%20prepared-for%20events%20in%20the%20flight%20deck%2C%20according%20to%20Allright.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20any%20pilot%20operates%20an%20aircraft%20on%20any%20given%20day%2C%20they%20run%20through%20what%20to%20do%20in%20case%20of%20an%20engine%20failure%2C%20Allright%20told%20us.%20This%20means%20that%20if%20an%20engine%20failure%20were%20to%20ever%20happen%2C%20they%20are%20already%20prepared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20all%20commercial%20aircraft%20are%20able%20to%20fly%20with%20just%20one%20engine%2C%20in%20case%20the%20other%20fails.%20When%20an%20aircraft%20is%20taxiing%20to%20its%20take-off%20position%2C%20for%20example%2C%20it%20almost%20always%20uses%20only%20one%20engine%20to%20save%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20an%20airplane%20can%20still%20glide%20up%20to%20100%20miles%20even%20if%20both%20engines%20are%20off%2C%20Allright%20told%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20case%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-show-a320-jet-that-crash-landed-the-hudson-river-2022-1%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3EUS%20Airways%20Flight%201549%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20safely%20landed%20in%20the%20Hudson%20River%20in%202009%20after%20a%20flock%20of%20birds%20flew%20into%20both%20of%20its%20engines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20both%20engines%20were%20damaged%2C%20the%20wings%20of%20the%20aircraft%20were%20still%20capable%20of%20producing%20lift%20and%20were%20therefore%20able%20to%20glide%2C%20and%20land%20on%20the%20water%20with%20no%20loss%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221717%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22british%20airways%20flying%20with%20confidence%20course%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ad6b238ed31300199e6e14%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221288%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBritish%20Airways%20organises%20a%20Flying%20with%20Confidence%20course%20five%20times%20a%20year.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Ankel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E5.%20Pilots%20are%20highly-trained%20and%20qualified%20professionals%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20tip%20might%20sound%20simple%2C%20but%20learning%20about%20how%20well%20pilots%20are%20actually%20trained%20really%20helped%20me%20combat%20my%20fear%20of%20flying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20that%20commercial%20pilots%20are%20among%20the%20most%20regulated%20professions%20in%20the%20world.%20Not%20only%20is%20the%20training%20to%20become%20a%20commercial%20airline%20pilot%20very%20intensive%2C%20but%20they%20also%20have%20to%20undergo%20regular%20checks%20and%20tests%20as%20they%20continue%20to%20fly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20British%20Airways%2C%20for%20example%2C%20every%20pilot%20has%20to%20do%20a%20medical%20and%20technical%20exam%20every%20year.%20They%20also%20have%20to%20regularly%20do%20training%20in%20a%20flight%20simulator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20the%20pilots%20I%20spoke%20to%20during%20the%20course%20reassured%20me%20over%20and%20over%20again%20that%20safety%20is%20in%20everyone's%20interest!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E6.%20Breathing%20is%20key%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20takeaways%20from%20the%20course%20was%20how%20to%20control%20my%20fear%20of%20flying%20through%20breath%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20forcing%20our%20body%20to%20slow%20down%20its%20breathing%2C%20it%20will%20start%20to%20relax.%20In%20particular%2C%20we%20were%20taught%20a%20breathing%20technique%20that%20Allright%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BBreathe%20and%20Squeeze.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20involves%20first%20breathing%20air%20out%20of%20your%20mouth%20before%20sucking%20it%20back%20in%20through%20your%20nose.%20While%20you%20inhale%2C%20you%20also%20squeeze%20the%20glutes%20and%20pelvic%20area.%20The%20exercise%20will%20not%20only%20slow%20your%20heart%20rate%20but%20will%20also%20reduce%20muscle%20tension.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiaphragmic%20breathing%2C%20otherwise%20known%20as%20belly%20breathing%2C%20is%20another%20way%20to%20force%20your%20body%20to%20relax.%20This%20involves%20breathing%20into%20the%20lower%20part%20of%20the%20lungs%2C%20which%20will%20fill%20up%20the%20diaphragm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlacing%20your%20hands%20around%20the%20tummy%20or%20ribcage%20and%20feeling%20the%20expansion%20and%20compression%20of%20the%20breath%20is%20also%20useful.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20life-changing%20experience%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20tips%20are%20only%20a%20fraction%20of%20all%20of%20the%20things%20I%20learned%20in%20the%20course%2C%20which%20ultimately%20left%20me%20feeling%20empowered%20and%20ready%20for%20my%20next%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20having%20the%20opportunity%20to%20ask%20pilots%20as%20many%20questions%20as%20I%20wanted%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20stupid%20they%20were%2C%20was%20extremely%20helpful%20for%20my%20anxious%20brain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20already%20have%20a%20few%20holidays%20booked%2C%20so%20am%20already%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20day%20I%20can%20sit%20through%20turbulence%20with%20no%20problems%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhere-are-6-things-nervous-passenger-should-know-before-flying-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689586648000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ad44fd8ed31300199e6877%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhere-are-6-things-nervous-passenger-should-know-before-flying-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20took%20British%20Airways'%20Flying%20with%20Confidence%20course%2C%20which%20teaches%20nervous%20air%20passengers%20how%20to%20best%20deal%20with%20their%20anxieties%20around%20flying.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sankel%40businessinsider.com%20(Sophia%20Ankel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhere-are-6-things-nervous-passenger-should-know-before-flying-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SRK%20unveils%20Nayanthara's'Jawan'%20poster%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689586485000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101824680%2Cimgsize-35650.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-unveils-nayantharas-feisty-jawan-character-poster-pic-inside%2Farticleshow%2F101824612.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F101824612.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20on%20Monday%20dropped%20the%20first%20poster%20of%20Nayanthara's%20character%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Atlee%20directorial%20%26quot%3BJawan%26quot%3B.%20The%20actor%20introduced%20his%20leading%20lady%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20thunder%20that%20co