ng%20AAP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20is%20unlikely%20to%20face%20any%20trouble%20getting%20its%20ordinance%20on%20the%20control%20of%20Delhi's%20bureaucrats%20through%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20where%20it%20does%20not%20have%20a%20majority%2C%20despite%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20securing%20the%20Congress's%20support%20on%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20currently%20in%20a%20strong%20position%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20unless%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20or%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20of%20Jagan%20Reddy%20have%20other%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20BJP%20members%20and%20six%20Trinamool%20MPs%20are%20set%20to%20be%20elected%20unchallenged%20to%2011%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seats%20after%20nominations%20closed%20today%20without%20any%20opposing%20candidates.%20The%20Congress%20is%20likely%20to%20lose%20one%20seat%20and%20drop%20to%2030%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20is%20set%20to%20gain%20one%20and%20bolster%20its%20count%20to%2093.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven%20seats%20in%20the%20245-member%20Rajya%20Sabha%20will%20be%20vacant%20after%20July%2024%20-%20four%20seats%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20two%20nominated%20and%20one%20vacant%20seat%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20next%20week%2C%20when%20the%20monsoon%20session%20is%20under%20way%2C%20the%20total%20seats%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20will%20come%20down%20to%20238%20and%20the%20majority%20mark%20will%20be%20120.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20allies%20in%20the%20ruling%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20will%20have%20105%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20also%20confident%20of%20the%20support%20of%20five%20nominated%20and%20two%20independent%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20number%20of%20members%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20government%20will%20be%20112%2C%20which%20is%20eight%20short%20of%20the%20new%20majority%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20expects%20support%20from%20Mayawati's%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20Secular%20and%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%2C%20which%20have%20an%20MP%20each%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20opposition%2C%20105%20members%20are%20against%20the%20Delhi%20Ordinance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20clear%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20test%2C%20the%20government%20will%20need%20help%20from%20the%20BJD%20and%20YSRCP%2C%20which%20have%20nine%20members%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJD%20has%20said%20it%20will%20decide%20when%20the%20bill%20to%20replace%20the%20Delhi%20ordinance%20comes%20up%20for%20discussion%20and%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YSRCP's%20Jagan%20Reddy%20is%20also%20yet%20to%20reveal%20his%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20both%20parties%20had%20walked%20out%20during%20a%20vote%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20a%20controversial%20bill.%20This%20helped%20the%20government%20by%20bringing%20down%20the%20majority%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20do%20the%20same%20this%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20will%20surpass%20the%20majority%20mark%2C%20which%20will%20have%20dropped%20to%20111.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20will%20be%20in%20trouble%20only%20if%20the%20two%20parties%20vote%20against%20the%20bill%2C%20which%20does%20not%20seem%20likely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20has%20the%20option%20of%20nominating%20two%20members%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20before%20voting%20on%20the%20Delhi%20Ordinance%2C%20increasing%20its%20tally%20to%20114.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fight%20between%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20Delhi%20over%20the%20control%20of%20services%20in%20the%20capital%20escalated%20after%20the%20Centre%20passed%20a%20special%20order%20to%20override%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20that%20said%20the%20elected%20government%20in%20Delhi%2C%20not%20the%20Centre%2C%20has%20control%20over%20the%20transfer%20and%20appointments%20of%20bureaucrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20rallying%20point%20for%20the%20opposition%2C%20meeting%20with%20numerous%20party%20leaders%20nationwide%20for%20support%20and%20also%20making%20it%20a%20condition%20for%20AAP's%20participation%20in%20opposition%20meetings%20that%20include%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689586020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2F93ihk9bg_vk-saxena-arvind-kejriwal-pti_625x300_17_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-centre-can-pass-delhi-ordinance-despite-congress-backing-aap-4214375%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20is%20unlikely%20to%20face%20any%20trouble%20passing%20its%20ordinance%20on%20the%20control%20of%20Delhi's%20bureaucrats%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20where%20it%20does%20not%20have%20a%20majority%2C%20despite%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20getting%20the%20Congress's%20support%20on%20the%20subject.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-centre-can-pass-delhi-ordinance-despite-congress-backing-aap-4214375%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-centre-can-pass-delhi-ordinance-despite-congress-backing-aap-4214375%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-centre-can-pass-delhi-ordinance-despite-congress-backing-aap-4214375%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Uniting%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20His%20Uncle%20Is%20Key%20To%20BJP's%20Bihar%20Plan%20For%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20repeated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchirag-paswan-pashupati-kumar-paras-ram-vilas-paswan-uncle-vs-nephew-again-in-bihars-lok-janshakti-party-bjp-wants-a-merger-4213597%5C%22%3Epush%20to%20unite%20the%20warring%20uncle%20and%20nephew%20duo%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20long-time%20ally%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20is%20part%20of%20its%20larger%20strategy%20to%20stitch%20together%20a%20coalition%20of%20caste%20groups%20formidable%20enough%20to%20challenge%20the%20mighty%20%26quot%3BLuv-Kush%26quot%3B%20(Kurmi-Koeri)%20and%20%26quot%3BMuslim-Yadav%26quot%3B%20alliance%20powering%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20BJP%20has%20slowly%20but%20steadily%20tried%20to%20court%20allies%20after%20it%20found%20itself%20in%20dire%20straits%20following%20the%20sudden%20break-up%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20boss%20Nitish%20Kumar%20last%20year.%20While%20walking%20out%20of%20the%20NDA%20alliance%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20also%20took%20away%20all%20other%20parties%20in%20Bihar%2C%20leaving%20only%20the%20Pashupati%20Paras%20faction%20of%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20as%20a%20BJP%20ally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDenting%20the%20%26quot%3BLuv-Kush%26quot%3B%20vote%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20of%20Samrat%20Choudhary%2C%20a%20Kushwaha%20(traditionally%20Koeri%20caste)%20leader%20who%20sports%20a%20turban%20and%20claims%20he%20will%20remove%20it%20only%20after%20dethroning%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20as%20the%20state%20BJP%20chief%20is%20also%20in%20line%20with%20its%20ambition%20to%20break%20away%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%20votes%20from%20the%20JD(U).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKurmi%20and%20Koeri%20castes%2C%20largely%20comprising%20landowning%20farmers%20and%20vegetable%20growers%2C%20which%20together%20constitute%20about%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20Bihar's%20population%2C%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20traditionally%20sided%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20By%20projecting%20a%20Kushwaha%20leader%20as%20the%20Chief%20Ministerial%20face%20for%20the%20next%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20to%20be%20held%20soon%20after%20next%20year's%20big%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20angling%20to%20slice%20off%20a%20core%20voter%20base%20from%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Choudhary%20has%20been%20with%20both%20the%20JD(U)%20and%20RJD%20before%20he%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%202017.%20Son%20of%20former%20minister%20Shakuni%20Choudhury%2C%20he%20was%20considered%20a%20blue-eyed-boy%20of%20RJD%20patriarch%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20and%20was%20inducted%20into%20the%20state%20cabinet%20when%20he%20wasn't%20even%2025-years-old%2C%20but%20was%20later%20dumped%20after%20controversy%20over%20his%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rajput%2C%20Bhumihar%2C%20Kayasth%2C%20Kurmi%2C%20Brahmin%2C%20Dalit%2C%20Muslim%20and%20Yadav%20communities%20have%20all%20had%20representatives%20as%20Chief%20Ministers%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20Kushwaha%20community%20is%20yet%20to%20see%20a%20representative%20hold%20the%20top%20job%2C%20baring%20a%20five-day%20stint%20of%20Satish%20Prasad%20Singh%2C%20who%20held%20the%20post%20for%20just%20five%20days%20in%201968.%20Samrat%20Choudhary%2C%20who%2C%20unlike%20his%20predecessors%2C%20is%20very%20aggressive%20in%20his%20attack%20on%20the%20government%2C%20is%20being%20groomed%20for%20the%20top%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnda-meeting-opposition-meeting-2024-elections-ndas-30-vs-24-in-opposition-show-of-strength-for-2024-polls-on-tuesday-4212344%5C%22%3Einvitation%20to%20Upendra%20Singh%20Kushwaha%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Samta%20Party%20for%20the%20big%20NDA%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%20tomorrow%20is%20another%20move%20aimed%20to%20cut%20down%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20considered%20the%20shadow%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Bihar%2C%20and%20a%20close%20confidante%20of%20JD(U)%20boss%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20Ramchandra%20Prasad%20Singh%2C%20or%20RCP%20Singh%2C%20joining%20the%20BJP%20in%20May%20after%20being%20denied%20renomination%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20which%20forced%20him%20to%20quit%20the%20Union%20cabinet%2C%20is%20another%20significant%20win%20for%20the%20BJP.%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20RCP%20Singh%20are%20both%20from%20the%20Nalanda%20district%20and%20Kurmi%20caste%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20might%20try%20to%20pit%20the%20two%20against%20each%20other%20to%20eat%20into%20Mr%20Kumar's%20electoral%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDalits%2C%20other%20caste%20calculations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Most%20Backward%20Castes%20which%20had%20voted%20for%20the%20NDA%20in%20the%20last%20elections%20are%20supporters%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20and%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20walked%20away%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20non-Yadav%20OBCs%20(Other%20Backward%20Castes)%2C%20Dalits%2C%20Yadavs%2C%20and%20Muslims%20are%20firmly%20behind%20Tejashwi%20Yadav's%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal.%20It%20is%20here%20that%20the%20BJP%20wants%20the%20re-unification%20of%20late%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan's%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20--%20now%20split%20into%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20and%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party.%20A%20united%20LJP%2C%20which%20commands%20significant%20Dalit%20and%20Mahadalit%20votes%2C%20and%20getting%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%20and%20his%20Hindustani%20Awam%20Morcha%20into%20the%20NDA%2C%20will%20give%20the%20BJP%20a%20foothold%20into%20the%20Dalit%20voter%20base.%20Mr%20Manjhi%20has%20also%20been%20invited%20to%20the%20NDA%20meeting%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukesh%20Sahani%20of%20the%20Vikassheel%20Insaan%20Party%20has%20also%20been%20invited%20to%20join%20the%20NDA.%20A%20leader%20of%20the%20Nishads%20(traditionally%20fisherpeople)%2C%20who%20account%20for%20around%2015%25%20of%20the%20population%20of%20Bihar%20and%20UP%2C%20Mr%20Sahani%20can%20steer%20EBC%20votes%20away%20from%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20However%2C%20Mukesh%20Sahani%2C%20popularly%20called%20'Son%20of%20Mallah'%2C%20harbouring%20Chief%20Ministerial%20ambitions%20could%20be%20a%20wrench%20in%20the%20works%20for%20BJP's%20carefully%20curated%20caste%20arithmetic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2040%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies%20in%20Bihar.%20In%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20won%20a%20thumping%20victory%2C%20bagging%2039%20seats.%20While%20the%20RJD%2C%20the%20then%20main%20opposition%20party%20in%20Bihar%2C%20got%20no%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%20managed%20to%20get%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20had%20won%2017%20seats%2C%20JD(U)%2016%2C%20and%20LJP%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689586020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Foccca438_chirag-paswan-ram-chandra-paswan-ani-650_650x400_17_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaste-politics-in-bihar-bjp-nitish-kumar-rjd-jdu-tejashwi-yadav-why-uniting-chirag-paswan-his-uncle-is-key-to-bjps-bihar-plan-for-2024-4214070%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP's%20repeated%20push%20to%20unite%20the%20warring%20uncle%20and%20nephew%20duo%20of%20long-time%20ally%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20is%20part%20of%20its%20larger%20strategy%20to%20stitch%20together%20a%20coalition%20of%20caste%20groups%20formidable%20enough%20to%20challenge%20the%20Mahagathbandhan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaste-politics-in-bihar-bjp-nitish-kumar-rjd-jdu-tejashwi-yadav-why-uniting-chirag-paswan-his-uncle-is-key-to-bjps-bihar-plan-for-2024-4214070%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaste-politics-in-bihar-bjp-nitish-kumar-rjd-jdu-tejashwi-yadav-why-uniting-chirag-paswan-his-uncle-is-key-to-bjps-bihar-plan-for-2024-4214070%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaste-politics-in-bihar-bjp-nitish-kumar-rjd-jdu-tejashwi-yadav-why-uniting-chirag-paswan-his-uncle-is-key-to-bjps-bihar-plan-for-2024-4214070%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20AI%20boom%20is%20screwing%20over%20Gen%20Z%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20AI%20ha