.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-centre-can-pass-delhi-ordinance-despite-congress-backing-aap-4214375%5C%22%3Eunlikely%20to%20face%20any%20trouble%20getting%20its%20ordinance%20through%20Rajya%20Sabha%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20it%20does%20not%20have%20a%20majority%2C%20despite%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20securing%20the%20Congress's%20support%20on%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689585540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fqharjlh_arvind-kejriwal-vk-saxena_625x300_08_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flt-governor-delhi-chief-minister-have-to-rise-above-political-bickering-supreme-court-4214482%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20suggestion%20to%20break%20the%20impasse.%20Can%20the%20LG%20and%20CM%20sit%20down%20and%20give%20an%20agreeable%20candidate%3F%20So%20that%20the%20person%20can%20be%20appointed%20for%20DERC%20(Delhi%20Electricity%20Regulatory%20Commission)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flt-governor-delhi-chief-minister-have-to-rise-above-political-bickering-supreme-court-4214482%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flt-governor-delhi-chief-minister-have-to-rise-above-political-bickering-supreme-court-4214482%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flt-governor-delhi-chief-minister-have-to-rise-above-political-bickering-supreme-court-4214482%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Three%20Held%20for%20Beating%20Up%20Muslim%20Man%2C%20Forcing%20Him%20to%20Chant%20'Jai%20Shri%20Ram'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17144246%2FImage-16-07-23-at-8.08-PM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%2032-year-old%20man%20was%20attacked%20with%20swords%2C%20iron%20rods%2C%20and%20