de%20Bharat%20train%20at%20his%20home%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20want%20us%20to%20decide%20where%20the%20Vande%20Bharat%20train%20will%20stop%3F%20Should%20we%20schedule%20a%20Delhi-Mumbai%20Rajdhani%20stop%20next%3F%20This%20is%20a%20policy%20matter%2C%20go%20to%20the%20authorities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CJI%20said%2C%20rebuking%20the%20petitioner%20PT%20Sheejish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20argued%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20should%20at%20least%20ask%20the%20government%20to%20consider%20this%20representation%2C%20but%20the%20CJI%20said%20that%20he%20would%20not%20interfere%2C%20as%20it%20would%20seem%20that%20the%20court%20took%20cognisance%20in%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20had%20alleged%20that%20even%20though%20there%20was%20a%20proposal%20to%20allot%20a%20stop%20for%20the%20new%20'Vande%20Bharat'%20at%20Tirur%2C%20it%20didn't%20fructify%20without%20any%20reason.%20Despite%20Malappuram%20being%20densely%20populated%20and%20many%20people%20depending%20on%20train%20services%20for%20their%20travel%20purposes%2C%20a%20stop%20has%20not%20been%20allotted%20for%20the%20district%2C%20the%20petitioner%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETirur%20was%20allotted%20a%20stop%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Malappuram%20district%2C%20but%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20called%20back%20the%20stop%20and%20instead%20another%20railway%20station%20--%20Shornur%20in%20the%20Palakkad%20district%20--%20was%20allotted%2C%20which%20is%20roughly%2056%20km%20away%20from%20Tirur%2C%20the%20petitioner%20said%2C%20alleging%20it%20was%20done%20for%20political%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20failure%20to%20allot%20a%20stop%20at%20Tirur%20Railway%20Station%20is%20an%20injustice%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Malappuram%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20ignoring%20their%20requests%20and%20demands%20causes%20great%20prejudice%2C%20he%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20stops%20to%20be%20provided%20for%20a%20train%20is%20a%20matter%20that%20has%20to%20be%20determined%20by%20the%20Railways.%20No%20person%20has%20a%20vested%20right%20to%20demand%20that%20a%20particular%20train%20should%20stop%20at%20a%20particular%20station%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20if%20every%20individual%20or%20public-spirited%20person%20in%20every%20district%20starts%20clamouring%20or%20demanding%20a%20stop%20to%20be%20provided%20at%20a%20railway%20station%20of%20their%20choice%2C%20the%20purpose%20of%20setting%20up%20high%20speed%20trains%20would%20itself%20be%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRailway%20stops%20are%20not%20to%20be%20provided%20on%20demands%20based%20on%20personal%20or%20vested%20interests%2C%20especially%20for%20high%20speed%20express%20trains%20like%20Vande%20Bharat%20train.%20If%20stops%20are%20provided%20on%20demand%20by%20the%20public%2C%20the%20term%20express%20train%20will%20itself%20become%20a%20misnomer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vande%20Bharat%20train%20in%20question%20runs%20from%20one%20end%20of%20the%20state%20--%20Thiruvananthapuram%20--%20to%20the%20other%20end%20--%20Kasaragod%20--%20and%20back%20on%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20of%20Kerala%20at%20Ernakulam%20had%20earlier%20dismissed%20the%20petition%20on%20the%20view%20that%20courts%20cannot%20interfere%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20providing%20stops%20for%20railway%20trains%2C%20and%20that%20it%20is%20purely%20within%20the%20discretion%20and%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20railways.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689585300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fp4eevs58_supreme-court_625x300_24_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftirur-railway-station-vande-bharat-express-kerala-turned-this-into-post-office-supreme-court-to-lawyer-over-unusual-request-4214418%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20High%20Court%20of%20Kerala%20at%20Ernakulam%20had%20earlier%20dismissed%20the%20petition%20on%20