%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Ffrom-meeting-suresh-raina-as-a-ball-boy-to-maiden-india-call-up-the-tilak-varma-story%2Farticleshow%2F101822932.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20first-time%20property%20investor%20who%20grew%20my%20portfolio%20to%20%245.5%20million%20in%203%20years.%20Here's%20how%20I%20did%20it%20with%20minimal%20savings.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221090%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alfred%20Dzadey%2C%20founder%20of%20Real%20Property%20Ventures%2C%20outside%20one%20of%20his%20investment%20properties%20in%20Coventry.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64afc2f84031de0019eae3e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22817%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlfred%20Dzadey%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Real%20Property%20Ventures%2C%20outside%20one%20of%20his%20investment%20properties%20in%20Coventry%2C%20England.%3Cp%3EAlfred%20Dzadey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAlfred%20Dzadey%2C%2029%2C%20bought%20his%20first%20property%20in%202020%20and%20renovated%20it%20into%20an%20HMO%20in%20five%20months.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20sought%20loans%20to%20finance%20his%20investments%2C%20then%20renovated%2C%20refinanced%2C%20and%20rented%20the%20properties.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20now%20has%20a%20portfolio%20worth%20%245.5%20million%20that%20generates%20tens%20of%20thousands%20in%20rent%20a%20month.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Alfred%20Dzadey%2C%20a%20real-estate%20investor%20who%20lives%20in%20Coventry%2C%20England%2C%20about%20building%20his%20portfolio.%20Insider%20has%20verified%20Dzadey's%20rental%20income.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20pursued%20a%20degree%20in%20aerospace%20engineering.%20After%20graduating%2C%20I%20realized%20my%20degree%20wasn't%20going%20to%20help%20me%20get%20wealthy%20young%2C%20as%20I'd%20hoped.%20I%20started%20researching%20how%20rich%20people%20built%20their%20wealth%20and%20found%20that%20owning%20real%20estate%20was%20a%20key%20factor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%20I%20was%2025%20and%20worked%20as%20a%20project%20manager%20for%20Jaguar%20Land%20Rover.%20I%20invested%20%C2%A325%2C000%20of%20my%20savings%20in%20in-person%20real-estate%20courses%20a%20friend%20recommended.%20The%20course%20gave%20me%20the%20confidence%20and%20knowledge%20to%20eventually%20build%20a%20real-estate%20portfolio%20worth%20%C2%A34.2%20million%2C%20or%20about%20%245.5%20million%2C%20in%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20asking%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20colleagues%20who%20knew%20how%20serious%20I%20was%20about%20real%20estate%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20invest%20with%20me.%20I%20told%20them%20I'd%20pay%20them%20the%20initial%20amount%20they%20loaned%20me%20plus%20a%20fixed%20interest%20rate%20higher%20than%20what%20their%20money%20would%20earn%20in%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20later%20I'd%20collected%20%C2%A3150%2C000%20from%20four%20investors%20and%20drafted%20loan%20agreements%20with%20each%20of%20them.%20I'd%20pay%20them%20back%20over%2012%20months%2C%20starting%20when%20they%20signed%20the%20loan%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFigure%20out%20what%20you're%20comfortable%20investing%20and%20fundraise%20your%20down%20payment%20and%20renovation%20costs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20magic%20number%20to%20start%20real-estate%20investing%2C%20but%20securing%20the%20capital%20for%20a%20down%20payment%2C%20about%2025%25%20to%2035%25%20of%20a%20property's%20value%2C%20is%20a%20good%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20in%20my%20network%20had%20shared%20which%20property%20investments%20were%20working%20for%20them.%20Using%20that%20knowledge%20and%20help%20from%20a%20local%20agent%2C%20I%20purchased%20my%20first%20property%20in%20February%202020%3A%20a%20mid-terrace%20house%20in%20Coventry%2C%20West%20Midlands%2C%20for%20%C2%A3225%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20invested%20in%20this%20house%20because%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20make%20a%20good%20HMO%3A%20a%20house%20of%20multiple%20occupancy.%20I%20used%20%C2%A360%2C000%20of%20the%20money%20I'd%20collected%20as%20a%20down%20payment%20for%20the%20home.%20In%20April%202020%2C%20my%20work%20contract%20was%20terminated%20due%20to%20COVID.%20I%20decided%20it%20was%20time%20to%20prove%20I%20could%20make%20real-estate%20investing%20a%20full-time%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tapped%20my%20property-investor%20network%20for%20referrals%20for%20trusted%20contractors%20and%20put%20the%20remaining%20%C2%A390%2C000%20toward%20refurbishing%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20renovations%20were%20completed%20in%20five%20months.%20We%20had%20the%20house%20revalued%2C%20and%20the%20value%20had%20increased%20from%20%C2%A3225%2C000%20to%20%C2%A3360%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'Buy%2C%20renovate%2C%20refinance%2C%20and%20rent'%20is%20a%20lucrative%20strategy%20to%20scale%20fast%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20strategy%20became%20clear%3A%20purchase%20a%20property%2C%20refurbish%20it%20so%20it%20gains%20value%2C%20then%20use%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20amount%20I%20owed%20the%20bank%20and%20the%20value%20of%20the%20property%20to%20recycle%20into%20the%20next%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20aim%20wasn't%20ever%20to%20sell%20for%20a%20quick%20return.%20My%20long-term%20goal%20was%20to%20hold%20the%20properties%20and%20build%20equity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20month%20after%20the%20refurbishments%20were%20complete%2C%20I%20started%20renting%20the%20property%20for%20%C2%A33%2C500%20a%20month.%20After%20bills%20and%20expenditures%2C%20my%20profit%20was%20around%20%C2%A31%2C400.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20the%20equity%20%E2%80%94%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20house's%20worth%20and%20the%20balance%20I%20owed%20to%20the%20bank%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20first%20property%20to%20purchase%20my%20second%20one.%20I%20paid%20back%20all%20my%20investors%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%2012-month%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20paid%20back%20the%20investors%2C%20I%20had%20to%20raise%20more%20money%2C%20since%20I%20was%20working%20on%20several%20projects%20in%20parallel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20each%20new%20property%20I%20wanted%20to%20flip%2C%20I%20assessed%20how%20much%20capital%20I%20needed%20and%20raised%20it%2C%20as%20required%2C%20from%20my%20network.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20the%20equity%20on%20the%20property%20I%20was%20completing%20was%20%C2%A350%2C000%20short%20of%20what%20I%20needed%20to%20purchase%20the%20next%20property%2C%20I'd%20reach%20out%20to%20my%20network%20and%20crowdsource%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20continued%20until%20I%20had%20eight%20properties%20to%20my%20name%20in%20three%20years.%20I%20renovated%20each%20one%20and%20then%20rented%20it%20out%2C%20using%20the%20rental%20income%20to%20reinvest%20in%20other%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20more%20properties%20I%20purchased%2C%20the%20more%20I%20learned%20about%20what%20works%20well%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20use%20the%20same%20property-management%20company%20to%20vet%20renters%20and%20keep%20the%20rent%20paid%20for%20all%20my%20properties%2C%20which%20saves%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20work.%20I%20use%20that%20time%20to%20find%20new%20opportunities%20and%20raise%20more%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20each%20purchase%20I%20learned%20which%20properties%20made%20lucrative%20investments.%20I%20favored%20properties%20closer%20to%20Coventry%20city%20center%20because%20of%20easy%20access%20to%20shops%2C%20amenities%2C%20and%20transport%20links%2C%20making%20them%20enticing%20for%20renters%20in%20all%20market%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20also%20research%20which%20types%20of%20rentals%20were%20in%20demand%20in%20an%20area%20before%20purchasing%20a%20property.%20For%20instance%2C%20an%20area%20with%20families%20wouldn't%20do%20as%20well%20renting%20out%20a%20house%20of%20multiple%20occupants%2C%20but%20an%20area%20with%20lots%20of%20students%20would.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20I%20researched%20how%20local%20authorities%20reacted%20to%20unit%20modifications%20in%20the%20area.%20Were%20they%20lenient%20about%20changes%3F%20Or%20did%20they%20make%20things%20difficult%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReturn%20on%20investment%20was%20always%20a%20driving%20factor.%20If%20a%20property%20was%20too%20expensive%20or%20cost%20too%20much%20to%20fix%2C%20that%20was%20a%20red%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%2C%20I%20bought%20a%20property%20with%20the%20plan%20to%20do%20a%20loft%20conversion%3B%20later%20I%20found%20out%20the%20roof%20needed%20to%20be%20replaced%20because%20it%20was%20caving%20in.%20In%20another%20instance%20I%20learned%20that%20damaged%20or%20diminished%20glaze%20on%20Victorian%20windows%20could%20cost%20up%20to%20%C2%A37%2C000%20to%20replace.%20I%20turned%20down%20projects%20requiring%20fixes%20to%20these%20types%20of%20windows%20and%20properties%20with%20a%20botched%20roof%20or%20those%20at%20risk%20of%20subsidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20gathered%20a%20team%20of%20builders%20to%20help%20me%20evaluate%20properties%20and%20alert%20me%20to%20concerns.%20I%20connected%20with%20them%20through%20my%20network%20of%20experienced%20investors%20and%20paid%20them%20per%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESites%20like%20Zoopla%20and%20Rightmove%20were%20helpful%20to%20identify%20potential%20investments%2C%20but%20nothing%20beats%20a%20strong%20relationship%20with%20a%20real-estate%20broker.%20Agents%20I'd%20worked%20with%20were%20soon%20calling%20me%20to%20offer%20off-market%20deals%20because%20they%20knew%20I%20was%20a%20credible%20and%20serious%20buyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20spreading%20the%20word%20to%20people%20I%20knew%20came%20in%20handy.%20For%20instance%2C%20I%20came%20across%20one%20property%20because%20a%20neighbor%20knew%20I%20was%20in%20real%20estate%20and%20offered%20it%20to%20me%20before%20listing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20nothing%20outvalues%20the%20importance%20of%20mentorship%20and%20learning.%20The%20book%20%26quot%3BThe%2010X%20Rule%26quot%3B%20taught%20me%20a%20lot.%20I%20also%20have%20mentors%20and%20coaches%20I%20rely%20on%20who%20I%20know%20through%20personal%20networking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENow%20I%20help%20others%20invest%20in%20real%20estate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20give%20real-estate%20classes%20and%20mentor%20others%20to%20secure%20projects%2C%20raise%20capital%2C%20and%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20grown%20my%20portfolio%20from%20one%20to%20eight%20properties%20within%20three%20years.%20My%20current%20portfolio's%20valuation%20is%20nearly%20%C2%A34.2%20million%2C%20with%20%C2%A31.2%20million%20of%20that%20comprising%20my%20equity%20and%20the%20rest%20belonging%20to%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20make%20about%20%C2%A325%2C000%20a%20month%20right%20now%2C%20and%20it%20will%20jump%20to%20nearly%20%C2%A330%2C000%20next%20money%20as%20I've%20just%20got%20tenants%20in%20a%20new%20set%20of%20flats.%20All%20my%20properties%20have%20healthy%20cash%20flow.%20Because%20of%20the%20desirable%20locations%2C%20generally%20when%20one%20tenant%20moves%20out%20of%20a%20property%20another%20moves%20in%20within%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20my%20real-estate%20journey.%20My%20plans%20include%20taking%20inspiration%20from%20the%20multifamily%20market%20in%20the%20US%20and%20replicating%20this%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproperty-investor-built-million-dollar-portfolio-no-savings-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689585038000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64afcddfc22d1a0019453e2c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproperty-investor-built-million-dollar-portfolio-no-savings-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alfred%20Dzadey%2C%20a%20first-time%20property%20investor%2C%20bought%20an%20HMO%20in%20Coventry%2C%20England%2C%20after%20crowdsourcing%20loans%20from%20family%20and%20friends%20in%202020.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Salina%20Jivani)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproperty-investor-built-million-dollar-portfolio-no-savings-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CEO%20Receives%203%2C000%20Resumes%20In%2048%20Hours%3A%20%5C%22How%20Bad%20Is%20The%20Job%20Market%3F%5C%22%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20founder%20and%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20(CEO)%20of%20a%20start-up%20said%20that%20he%20received%20more%20than%203%2C000%20resumes%20in%2048%20hours%20for%20job%20postings%20on%20the%20company%20website.%20Kartik%20Mandaville%20shared%20the%20update%20on%20Twitter%20where%20his%20post%20became%20a%20hit%2C%20attracting%20close%20to%201.5%20lakh%20views.%20Mr%20Mandaville%20also%20said%20the%20huge%20number%20of%20applications%20shows%20the%20current%20status%20of%20the%20job%20market.%20He%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Springworks%2C%20which%20provides%20software%20solutions%20for%20human%20resources%20sector.%20The%20company%20was%20established%20in%20the%20year%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReceived%20over%203K%20resumes%20in%20the%20last%2048%20hours%20just%20on%20our%20website%20-%20how%20bad%20is%20the%20job%20market%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mandaville%20said%20in%20his%20tweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EReceived%20over%203K%20resumes%20in%20the%20last%2048%20hours%20just%20on%20our%20website%20-%20how%20bad%20is%20the%20job%20market%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Kartik%20Mandaville%20(%40kar2905)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkar2905%2Fstatus%2F1680566500074176515%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20post%20started%20gaining%20traction%2C%20users%20posed%20questions%20for%20the%20entrepreneur.%20Mr%20Mandaville%20said%20he%20has%20so%20far%20received%20close%20to%2013%2C000%20applications%20for%20various%20roles%20in%20his%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mandaville%20also%20said%20that%20job%20postings%20were%20not%20promoted%20on%20any%20platform%20and%20only%20available%20on%20company%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20%26quot%3Bcurious%26quot%3B%20user%20asked%20about%20the%20roles%2C%20to%20which%20Mr%20Mandaville%20replied%20they%20are%20product%2C%20founder's%20office%20and%20software%20development%20engineer%2C%20among%20others.%20All%20these%20roles%20are%20remote%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20numbers%20swell%20primarily%20because%20of%20the%20word%20'remote'%20next%20to%20each%20opportunity%20in%20your%20listing.%20I'm%20wondering%20what%20would%20the%20numbers%20be%20if%20it%20was%20an%20on-site%20role%2C%26quot%3B%20commented%20one%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnemployment%20is%20at%20peak%2C%20young%20people%20are%20desperate%20for%20jobs%20even%20if%20it%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20what%20they%20learnt%20in%20college%2C%26quot%3B%20tweeted%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Springworks%20website%2C%20Mr%20Mandaville%20did%20his%20masters%20in%20Machine%20Learning%20from%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20University%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20Mr%20Mandaville%20started%20coding%20at%20the%20age%20of%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689584760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-09%2Fjob-application_650x400_81506413892.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstart-up-ceo-receives-3-000-resumes-in-48-hours-how-bad-is-the-job-market-4214522%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Springworks%20founder%20and%20CEO%20Kartik%20Mandaville%20also%20said%20that%20job%20postings%20were%20not%20promoted%20on%20any%20platform%20and%20only%20available%20on%20company%20website.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstart-up-ceo-receives-3-000-resumes-in-48-hours-how-bad-is-the-job-market-4214522%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstart-up-ceo-receives-3-000-resumes-in-48-hours-how-bad-is-the-job-market-4214522%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstart-up-ceo-receives-3-000-resumes-in-48-hours-how-bad-is-the-job-market-4214522%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20used%20TSA%20PreCheck%20for%20the%20first%20time%20this%20summer.%20I%20only%20travel%20a%20few%20times%20a%20year%2C%20but%20for%20%2478%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20worth%20it.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222736%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20couple%20take%20a%20selfie%20on%20the%20beach%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b16acbf9a2590019475951%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222052%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJules%20Rogers%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Marshall.%3Cp%3EJules%20Rogers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJules%20Rogers%20is%20a%20casual%20traveler%20who%20visits%20family%20in%20other%20states%20a%20few%20times%20a%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20decided%20to%20get%20TSA%20PreCheck%20before%20a%20trip%20to%20California%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20it%20was%20worth%20the%20%2478%20and%20the%20hour%20of%20her%20time%20to%20be%20stress-free%20at%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20love%20traveling.%20Dealing%20with%20delays%2C%20long%20lines%2C%20the%20possibility%20of%20forgetting%20something%2C%20and%20the%20feeling%20of%20being%20a%20sardine%20isn't%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20casual%20traveler%20who%20visits%20family%20in%20other%20states%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20year.%20I'd%20heard%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftried-clear-tsa-precheck-and-global-entry-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETSA%20PreCheck%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20improve%20the%20airport%20experience%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20go%20for%20it%20because%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20just%20didn't%20travel%20often%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20increasingly%20frequent%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworst-airline-horror-stories-summer-travel-chaos-airport-passengers-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enightmare%20airport%20scenarios%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20two%20upcoming%20trips%20on%20my%20calendar%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20TSA%20PreCheck%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20the%20TSA%20PreCheck%20process%20went%20for%20me%20as%20a%20first-time%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20approval%20process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tsa.gov%2Fprecheck%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20applied%20online%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20application%20is%20about%20four%20pages%20and%20asks%20you%20to%20fill%20out%20basic%20information%20like%20your%20name%2C%20address%2C%20and%20driver's-license%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20last%20page%20I%20booked%20an%20in-person%20appointment%20at%20a%20nearby%20enrollment%20center.%20The%20workers%20were%20ready%20for%20me%20when%20I%20walked%20in%20on%20time%2C%20and%20it%20took%20about%2020%20minutes%20to%20process%20my%20information.%20I%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20legal-name%20complications%20from%20having%20recently%20married%2C%20so%20it%20took%20a%20bit%20longer%20for%20me%20than%20it%20did%20for%20other%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20weeks%20later%2C%20I%20received%20my%20Known%20Traveler%20Number%20and%20added%20it%20to%20my%20flight%20ticket%20via%20the%20airline's%20app.%20Enrollment%20workers%20had%20told%20me%20it%20could%20sometimes%20take%20up%20to%20three%20months%20for%20the%20background%20check%20to%20come%20through%2C%20and%20my%20husband's%20KTN%20actually%20didn't%20come%20through%20in%20time%20for%20our%20flight%20on%20July%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20a%20plebeian%2C%20he%20had%20to%20go%20through%20the%20regular%20security%20line%20at%20the%20Portland%20airport%2C%20while%20I%20used%20the%20PreCheck%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20man%20in%20an%20airport%20security%20line%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b165cdf9a2590019475798%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarshall%2C%20in%20the%20blue%20hat%2C%20walking%20in%20the%20regular%20security%20line%20at%20the%20Portland%20airport.%3Cp%3EJules%20Rogers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20airport%20experience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20PreCheck%20for%20the%20first%20time%20to%20fly%20to%20a%20family%20event%20in%20San%20Diego.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20there%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20couple%20hundred%20folks%20in%20the%20regular%20security%20line%2C%20I%20walked%20almost%20straight%20to%20the%20front%20of%20the%20PreCheck%20queue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20one%20dad%20in%20front%20of%20me%20with%20his%20daughter.%20The%20TSA%20worker%20asked%20the%20daughter%20if%20she%20knew%20her%20dad's%20birthday.%20After%20she%20answered%20correctly%2C%20the%20dad%20laughed%20and%20thanked%20the%20worker%20for%20the%20smart%20check.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stepped%20up%20next%2C%20handing%20over%20my%20driver's%20license%20to%20scan.%20I%20didn't%20need%20my%20boarding%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20emptied%20my%20pockets%20of%20my%20phone%2C%20wallet%2C%20and%20sunglasses%2C%20put%20them%20