0expenses%20that%20add%20up.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202018%2C%20my%20boyfriend%20Nick%20and%20I%20traveled%20to%20Cambodia%20to%20teach%20English.%20At%20the%20time%20we%20were%20living%20out%20of%20our%20backpacks%20when%20I%20found%20van%20life%20videos%20on%20YouTube.%20I%20just%20remember%20thinking%2C%20wow%2C%20that%20would%20be%20such%20a%20cool%20way%20to%20travel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20seed%20that%20was%20planted%20in%20our%20heads%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20when%20we%20came%20home%2C%20it%20was%20something%20we%20wanted%20to%20pursue.%20Then%20after%20arriving%20back%20home%20in%20Canada%2C%20we%20began%20to%20build%20out%20our%20van.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Van%20ambulance%20conversion%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b1600cf9a25900194755a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERaychel%20and%20Nicks%20converted%20van.%3Cp%3ERaychel%20and%20Nick%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20loved%20the%20idea%20of%20being%20able%20to%20travel%2C%20and%20we%20knew%20it%20would%20allow%20us%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20expenses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20it%2C%20we%20began%20to%20pick%20up%20seasonal%20jobs%2C%20including%20working%20in%20an%20office%2C%20house%20sitting%2C%20and%20working%20for%20a%20brick%20and%20mortar%20business.%20Then%20when%20we%20had%20enough%20money%20saved%20up%2C%20we%20left%20our%20jobs%20and%20hit%20the%20road.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20we've%20lived%20out%20of%20our%20van%20for%20three%20years%2C%20we've%20learned%20a%20lot%20along%20the%20way.%20Although%20we%20wouldn't%20trade%20van%20life%20for%20anything%2C%20here%20are%20five%20things%20you%20should%20know%20before%20trying%20it%20for%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20Everyday%20tasks%20can%20be%20exhausting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20staying%20in%20a%20house%2C%20and%20you%20want%20a%20glass%20of%20water%2C%20you%20just%20head%20over%20to%20the%20tap%2C%20where%20people%20usually%20have%20an%20endless%20supply.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20take%20a%20shower%2C%20you%20might%20do%20it%20without%20thinking.%20But%2C%20when%20you%20live%20in%20a%20van%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20more%20intentional.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20always%20thinking%20about%20what%20you're%20doing%20next.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20your%20water%20tank%20is%20getting%20low%2C%20you%20have%20to%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Van%20interior%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b15b6bf9a2590019475442%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20interior%20of%20Raychel%20and%20Nick's%20van.%3Cp%3ERaychel%20and%20Nick%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3Ethink%20about%20where%20you're%20going%20to%20refill%20it.%C2%A0%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20all%20changes%20by%20the%20geographic%20location%20you're%20in.%20Are%20you%20off%20grid%3F%20Are%20you%20close%20to%20the%20city%3F%20Can%20you%20fill%20up%20your%20water%20tank%20right%20away%3F%20Or%2C%20maybe%20you%20will%20have%20to%20wait.%20This%20all%20changes%20your%20consumption.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20that%20are%20in%20the%20background%20for%20others%2C%20aren't%20in%20the%20background%20for%20us.%20You%20have%20to%20always%20think%20about%20how%20you're%20going%20to%20live%2C%20including%20how%20often%20you%20flush%20your%20toilet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20People%20often%20ask%20about%20how%20we%20use%20the%20toilet%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20have%20a%20compost%20toilet%20in%20our%20van%2C%20as%20those%20are%20%241200.%20But%2C%20we%20do%20have%20a%20Dometic%20Portable%20Toilet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20think%20of%20it%20like%20a%20toilet%20with%20a%20holding%20tank.%20It%20holds%20everything%20in%20a%20small%20tank%2C%20but%20then%20you%20have%20to%20head%20to%20a%20sanitation%20dump%20station%20and%20manually%20dump%20it.%20You%20can%20find%20those%20at%20rest%20stops%20along%20the%20way%2C%20or%20sometimes%20when%20you%20get%20gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20thinking%20about%20van%20life%2C%20how%20you%20will%20use%20the%20toilet%20is%20something%20to%20consider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20There%20are%20expenses%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20van%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22605%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Broken%20down%20van%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b157ff9751e300192a1a41%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22454%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20expenses%20is%20when%20your%20van%20breaks%20down.%3Cp%3ERaychel%20and%20Nick%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20be%20a%20cheaper%20way%20to%20live%2C%20but%20there%20are%20still%20costs.%20First%2C%20you%20of%20course%20have%20your%20gas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20cost%20will%20be%20determined%20by%20how%20much%20you%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20you%20have%20your%20car%20insurance%2C%20your%20oil%20changes%2C%20and%20another%20is%20a%20gym%20membership.%20While%20the%20gym%20might%20seem%20optional%2C%20that%20is%20where%20most%20who%20choose%20van%20life%20shower.%20For%20us%2C%20our%20breakdown%20looks%20like%20this%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERV%20insurance%3A%20%24133%20a%20month%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGym%20memberships%3A%20%2445.00%20a%20month%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELaundromat%3A%20%2415.00%20a%20month%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGas%3A%20%24800%20a%20month%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGroceries%3A%20%24520%20a%20month%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20biggest%20expense%2C%20van%20breakdowns.%20Once%20we%20were%20on%20a%20trip%20through%20the%20USA%2C%20and%20ours%20broke%20when%20we%20were%20in%20San%20Diego.%20It%20was%20stressful%2C%20as%20we%20were%20quoted%20%243%2C000%20which%20is%20%244%2C500%20Canadian%20dollars.%20For%20us%2C%20it%20was%20a%20huge%20loss%20because%20it%20took%20our%20emergency%20fund.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20your%20van%20breaks%20down%20it%20is%20never%20fun.%20On%20top%20of%20that%20expense%2C%20you%20have%20to%20think%2C%20where%20am%20I%20going%20to%20stay%3F%20Getting%20a%20hotel%20unexpectedly%20definitely%20adds%20to%20your%20expenses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20said%2C%20when%20purchasing%20a%20van%2C%20you%20have%20to%20consider%20breakdowns.%20While%20you%20might%20want%20a%20unique%20van%2C%20it%20is%20better%20to%20get%20one%20with%20an%20easy%20to%20fix%20engine%2C%20this%20means%20one%20that%20any%20mechanic%20can%20fix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20lucky%20with%20ours.%20Since%20it's%20an%20ambulance%20conversion%2C%20it%20has%20the%20typical%20chevy%20engine.%20It's%20cheap%20to%20source%20and%20most%20mechanics%20can%20work%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20social%20stigmas%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20misunderstanding%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20sustaining%20van%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20all%20have%20the%20same%20income%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20all%20have%20the%20same%20story.%20Some%20of%20us%20work%20remotely%2C%20some%20work%20a%20regular%209%20to%205%20job%2C%20and%20some%20live%20out%20of%20a%20van%20not%20to%20travel%2C%20but%20out%20of%20necessity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20personally%20do%20seasonal%20work.%20We%20mainly%20take%20on%20house%20sitting%20assignments%2C%20and%20other%20summer%20jobs.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20work%20at%20a%20normal%209%20to%205%20office%20job.%20Then%20once%20we%20have%20enough%20saved%20up%2C%20we%20begin%20our%20travels.%20It's%20a%20process%20that%20we%20do%20again%20and%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20think%2C%20people%20who%20participate%20in%20van%20life%20don't%20work%2C%20or%20we%20don't%20have%20real%20jobs.%20While%20some%20who%20live%20in%20their%20vans%20might%20be%20rich%2C%20or%20have%20trust%20funds%2C%20that's%20not%20true%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20The%20social%20stigmas%20are%20very%20loud%2C%20but%20the%20truth%20is%20just%20like%20everyone%20else%2C%20we%20are%20all%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5.%20We%20miss%20moments%20with%20our%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20to%20put%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20to%20maintain%20friendships%20and%20relationships.%20You%20have%20to%20make%20the%20time%2C%20and%20make%20the%20calls%2C%20in%20order%20to%20stay%20in%20touch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20you%20do%20van%20life%20or%20you're%20nomadic%2C%20it%20can%20be%20hard%20missing%20birthdays%2C%20or%20being%20away%20from%20your%20family.%20We%20miss%20things%20like%20our%20nieces%20first%20steps%2C%20or%20other%20big%20moments%20just%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20really%20important%20for%20us%20to%20message%20them%2C%20or%20facetime%20them%2C%20that%20way%20we%20can%20stay%20connected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20we%20have%20also%20made%20many%20friends%20on%20the%20road%2C%20who%20live%20a%20very%20similar%20lifestyle%20to%20us.%20Since%20we're%20all%20on%20wheels%2C%20we%20often%20meet%20up%20with%20each%20other%2C%20and%20we%20can%20usually%20do%20it%20within%20a%20matter%20of%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22827%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Van%20life%20couple%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b1588429e5fd00190efba7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERaychel%20and%20Nick%20traveling%20in%20their%20ambulance%20conversion.%3Cp%3ERaychel%20and%20Nick%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EIt's%20not%20all%20bad%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20van%20life%20has%20downsides%2C%20there%20are%20many%20positives%2C%20too.%20We%20love%20being%20a%20part%20of%20the%20van%20life%20community%20and%20we%20would%20not%20trade%20van%20life%20for%20the%20high%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20Vancouver.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20location%20freedom%2C%20but%20there's%20also%20financial%20freedom%2C%20too.%2