space%20in%20Indian%20politics%20to%20%E2%80%9Cremain%20neutral%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVenugopal%20said%20the%20Bengaluru%20meeting%20will%20be%20a%20continuity%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Csuccessful%20and%20fruitful%E2%80%9D%20meeting%20at%20Patna%20on%20June%2023.%20He%20said%20the%20Congress%20was%20only%20hosting%20the%20meeting%2C%20and%20that%20a%20common%20minimum%20agenda%20will%20be%20finalised%20only%20after%20each%20of%20the%20participating%20parties%20arrives%20at%20a%20consensus%20on%20all%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20participating%20parties%20are%20on%20a%20common%20ground%20that%20the%20opposition%20front%E2%80%99s%20primary%20aim%20is%20%E2%80%9Cto%20defend%20constitutional%20rights%20and%20independence%20of%20institutions%20that%20are%20under%20unprecedented%20attack%20under%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20regime%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20want%20to%20silence%20the%20opposition%20voices.%20Even%20as%20we%20meet%20here%2C%20a%20Tamil%20Nadu%20opposition%20leader%20is%20being%20raided%20by%20central%20agencies.%20The%20BJP%20government%20is%20misusing%20central%20agencies%20like%20ED%2C%20CBI%20to%20target%20opposition%20voices.%20They%20want%20to%20destabilise%20democratically%20elected%20governments%20by%20misusing%20central%20agencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20Venugopal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20disqualification%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20the%20biggest%20example%20of%20such%20misuse%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17133902%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-17-at-1.35.43-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17133902%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-17-at-1.35.43-PM.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17133902%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-17-at-1.35.43-PM-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663582%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20poster%20for%20the%20joint%20opposition%20meet%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Photo%3A%20Ajoy%20Ashirwad%20Mahaprashasta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20announcement%2C%20Venugopal%20that%20the%20opposition%20meeting%20will%20also%20chalk%20out%20a%20common%20floor%20strategy%20for%20the%20upcoming%20monsoon%20session%20of%20the%20Parliament%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20the%20first%20test%20to%20showcase%20unity%20in%20the%20opposition%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20here%20to%20attain%20power%2C%20but%20to%20move%20forward%20unitedly%20to%20challenge%20the%20attacks%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20on%20our%20democratic%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20Venugopal%20said%2C%20emphasising%20that%20the%20united%20opposition%20front%20will%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgame%20changer%E2%80%9D%20in%20Indian%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%20said%20that%20the%20Patna%20meeting%20and%20the%20ongoing%20meeting%20in%20Bengaluru%20has%20forced%20the%20BJP%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20again.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20shown%20only%20indifference%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20alliances%2C%20has%20now%20been%20forced%20by%20the%20opposition%20to%20think%20about%20the%20NDA%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20great%20beginning%2C%20a%20great%20start.%20The%20entire%20opposition%2C%20except%20a%20few%2C%20will%20be%20joining%20the%20meeting%20here.%20Joining%20ranks%20is%20a%20beginning.%20Thinking%20together%20is%20progress.%20The%20meeting%20will%20shape%20the%20future%20of%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shivakumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20lampooned%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20continued%20silence%20on%20the%20Manipur%20ethnic%20conflict%20that%20has%20continued%20for%20more%20than%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20question%20about%20a%20possible%20leader%20or%20a%20convenor%20of%20the%20front%2C%20both%20Venugopal%20and%20Ramesh%20asserted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cissues%E2%80%9D%20are%20more%20important%20in%20forging%20opposition%20unity%20than%20having%20one%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20enough%20leaders.%20But%20we%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20important%20issues%20that%20have%20brought%20us%20together%20and%20challenge%20the%20BJP.%20Our%20common%20agenda%20is%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20Venugopal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17133940%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-17-at-1.35.43-PM-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17133940%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-17-at-1.35.43-PM-1.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17133940%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-17-at-1.35.43-PM-1-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663583%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20leaders%20K.C.%20Venugopal%2C%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20Karnataka%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%20and%20Pawan%20Khera%20address%20the%20media.%20Photo%3A%20Ajoy%20Ashirwad%20Mahaprashasta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%20said%20that%20for%20all%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20claims%20of%20having%20strong%20leadership%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20spoken%20a%20word%20on%20the%20Manipur%20crisis%20even%20as%20the%20state%20is%20burning%20for%20over%20two%20months.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20primary%20idea%20is%20to%20deflect%20attention%20from%20more%20pertinent%20issues%20that%20the%20opposition%20has%20been%20raising.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20confusion%20through%20the%20morning%20of%20July%2017%20on%20whether%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20currently%20facing%20a%20crisis%20because%20of%20the%20defections%20of%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20top%20leaders%2C%20will%20attend%20the%20meeting%20or%20not%20was%20cleared%20by%20Pawar%20himself%20in%20his%20tweet%20declaring%20that%20he%20will%20land%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20July%2018%20to%20attend%20the%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20(BJP)%20can%20divide%20the%20parties.%20But%20people%20will%20not%20tolerate.%20They%20did%20the%20same%20in%20Karnataka%20earlier.%20They%20took%20away%20our%2015%20MLAs.%20They%20targeted%20him%20(pointing%20at%20Shivakumar).%20But%20people%20will%20not%20tolerate%20such%20practices.%20You%20saw%20how%20people%20responded%20in%20Karnataka%20elections.%20They%20will%20do%20the%20same%20in%20Maharashtra%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20Venugopal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689577864000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F28184951%2FUntitled-design-2023-06-23T204437.720-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcommon-agenda-electoral-strategy-opposition-parties-set-the-stage-for-bengaluru-meet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22K.C.%20Venugopal%20said%20that%20while%2017%20parties%20attended%20the%20last%20Patna%20meeting%20on%20June%2023%2C%2026%20parties%20will%20join%20the%20Bengaluru%20meeting.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcommon-agenda-electoral-strategy-opposition-parties-set-the-stage-for-bengaluru-meet%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Love%20Actually%E2%80%99%20Filmmaker%20Ri