E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0focuses%20on%20all%20that%20is%20connected%20and%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20on%20digital%20issues%2C%20policy%2C%20ideas%20and%20themes%20dominating%20the%20conversation%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Registration%20of%20Births%20and%20Deaths%20Act%201969%20is%20a%20simple%20law%20that%20was%20brought%20for%20registration%20of%20births%20and%20deaths%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20new%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mha.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FRBDComments_27102021.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eamendments%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20is%20proposing%20to%20make%20Aadhaar%20mandatory%20to%20track%20new%20births%20and%20deaths%20in%20any%20family.%20It%20is%20proposing%20to%20build%20a%20database%20of%20births%20and%20deaths%20and%20use%20it%20to%20update%20every%20other%20database%20in%20the%20government%2C%20from%20the%20National%20Population%20Register%2C%20to%20voter%20rolls%2C%20and%20the%20databases%20of%20ration%20card%2C%20passport%2C%20driving%20licence%20and%20Aadhaar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20move%20will%20essentially%20track%20every%20Indian%20human%20across%20their%20lifetime%20from%20birth%20to%20death.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%20proposes%20to%20also%20make%20birth%20certificates%20mandatory%20for%20joining%20schools%2C%20registration%20of%20votes%2C%20marriages%2C%20issuance%20of%20passports%2C%C2%A0%20in%20applications%20for%20government%20jobs%20and%20for%20pretty%20much%20anything%20else%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20wants.%20This%20is%20going%20to%20make%20Indians%20stand%20in%20queues%20the%20same%20way%20they%20did%20because%20of%20Aadhaar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20proposed%20amendments%20to%20this%2050-year-old%20law%20will%20turn%20a%20simple%20state%20exercise%20into%20a%20population%20controlling%20mechanism%20that%20can%20be%20used%20against%20every%20citizen.%20Every%20individual%20has%20the%20right%20to%20documentation%2C%20a%20birth%20certificate%20or%20other%20forms%20of%20identification%20which%20they%20need%20to%20lead%20a%20dignified%20life.%20History%20shows%20us%20this%20simple%20yet%20transformative%20exercise%20can%20be%20weaponised%20and%20used%20to%20identify%20populations%20that%20are%20different%20and%20non-conformative.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20National%20Intelligence%20Grid%20(NATGRID)%20was%20proposed%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20interlinking%20databases%20across%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20branches%20for%20surveillance%20of%20the%20population.%20While%20the%20proposal%20existed%2C%20without%20the%20Aadhaar%20project%2C%20inter-linking%20of%20databases%20and%20accessing%20real-time%20information%20on%20Indians%20was%20a%20challenge.%20Aadhaar%20solved%20this%20for%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20and%20it%20pushed%20the%20surveillance%20capacity%20of%20the%20state%20at%20population%20scale.%20This%20has%20been%20a%20major%20point%20of%20contention%20with%20Aadhaar%20and%20its%20associated%20projects%20including%20National%20Population%20Register%20and%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20linking%20of%20databases%20and%20creation%20of%20360%C2%B0%20profiles%20using%20Aadhaar%20has%20always%20been%20an%20issue%20that%20was%20challenged%20in%20courts%2C%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdata-protection-bill-arbitrary-provisions-right-to-privacy%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20agreeing%20and%20recognising%20Indians%E2%80%99%20fundamental%20right%20to%20privacy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20duly%20noted%20reasonable%20restrictions%20on%20various%20grounds%20like%20national%20security%20do%20apply.%20A%20lack%20of%20a%20privacy%20law%20or%20surveillance%20law%20has%20ignored%20any%20form%20of%20accountability%20on%20the%20executive.%20The%20upcoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fdata-protection-bull-proliferation-digital-india%5C%22%3EDigital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20gives%20complete%20exemptions%20to%20the%20executive%20on%20data%20collection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20very%20idea%20of%20these%20linking%20databases%20automatically%20allows%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20to%20use%20information%20submitted%20for%20a%20specific%20purpose%20to%20be%20used%20for%20a%20secondary%20purpose.%20The%20purpose%20of%20birth%20certificates%20is%20at%20best%20is%20to%20prove%20nationality%20and%20at%20worst%20to%20prove%20lineage%20to%20a%20parent.%20The%20weaponization%20of%20this%20information%20without%20clearly%20bringing%20in%20any%20surveillance%20reform%20is%20an%20illegitimate%20act%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcivil-registration-system-crs-data-census-2021-covid-death-birth%5C%22%3EThe%20Union%20Govt%20Is%20Yet%20to%20Release%20Data%20on%20Births%20and%20Deaths%20for%202021.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20What%20We%20Are%20Missing%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20odd%20that%20the%20government%20thinks%20mass%20surveillance%20of%20the%20entire%20population%20will%20somehow%20help%20secure%20our%20country.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Aadhaar%20project%20has%20only%20shown%20that%20large%20databases%20are%20full%20of%20noise%20with%20fraudulent%20data%20entries.%20The%20promise%20of%20biometrics%20and%20birth%20certificates%20helping%20bring%20security%20is%20a%20myth.%20Especially%20when%20the%20state%20has%20no%20clue%20how%20to%20control%20our%20borders%20and%20is%20unable%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20Manipur%20crisis%20while%20ordering%20the%20collection%20of%20biometrics%20of%20any%20potential%20foreigner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20linking%20of%20databases%20and%20their%20effects%20can%20easily%20be%20seen%20in%20southern%20states%20of%20Telangana%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fin-andhra-jaganmohan-reddy-ysrcp-volunteers-privacy-voters-tech%5C%22%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20the%20push%20for%20real-time%20governance%20has%20allowed%20the%20government%20to%20track%20residents%20from%20birth%20to%20death.%20There%20is%20active%20opposition%20for%20this%20set-up%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20with%20political%20parties%20questioning%20the%20scale%20of%20data%20collection%20as%20part%20of%20real-time%20governance.%20The%20real-time%20policing%20in%20Telangana%20shows%20how%20all%20the%20information%20collected%20for%20welfare%20is%20being%20shared%20to%20police%20for%20real-time%20surveillance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fkhadeer-khan-telangana-police-tech%5C%22%3EWhat%20Khadeer%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Death%20Says%20About%20Telangana%20Police%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Tech%20Revolution%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17121342%2FScreenshot-2023-07-17-at-12.13.2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17121342%2FScreenshot-2023-07-17-at-12.13.2.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17121342%2FScreenshot-2023-07-17-at-12.13.2-300x169.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17121342%2FScreenshot-2023-07-17-at-12.13.2-1024x576.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663543%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeyond%20the%20surveillance-minded%20nature%20of%20this%20entire%20setup%2C%20the%20most%20concerning%20part%20is%20the%20issue%20of%20birth%20certificates%20becoming%20as%20mandatory%20as%20Aadhaar%20for%20voter%20ID.%20This%20has%20serious%20consequences%20for%20electoral%20democracy.%20The%20creation%20of%20360%C2%B0%20profiles%20with%20Aadhaar%20and%20linking%20it%20with%20the%20voter%20ID%20has%20already%20affected%20elections%20with%20how%20political%20parties%20can%20micro-target%20voters%20and%20delete%20voters%20from%20electoral%20rolls.%20Not%20only%20does%20it%20make%20us%20vulnerable%20to%20electoral%20fraud%2C%20it%20also%20centralises%20the%20management%20of%20electoral%20rolls%20using%20Aadhaar%20and%20birth%20certificates.%20It%20will%20also%20lead%20to%20exclusion%20of%20voters%20causing%20challenges%20with%20representation%20mostly%20among%20marginalised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20of%20these%20issues%20were%20not%20clarified%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20during%20the%20Aadhaar%20judgement%20and%20are%20likely%20to%20come%20back%20to%20the%20court%20in%20future.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20this%20Bill%20puts%20in%20place%20a%20mechanism%20to%20continuously%20collect%20information%20from%20individuals%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20government%20still%20has%20to%20carry%20out%20large%20scale%20data%20collection%20drives%20to%20update%20this%20entire%20set-up.%20The%20Census%202021%20whenever%20it%20happens%20will%20be%20the%20place%20where%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20will%20push%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20this%20setup.%20It%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20Census%20Act%20does%20not%20allow%20any%20data%20sharing%2C%20while%20the%20present%20draft%20promotes%20data%20sharing%20across%20government%20departments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20proliferation%20of%20personal%20data%20across%20several%20departments%20is%20bound%20to%20leak%20and%20also%20cause%20unforeseen%20challenges%20that%20were%20similarly%20anticipated%20with%20Aadhaar.%20This%20bill%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20passed%20or%20not%2C%20does%20not%20stop%20the%20continuous%20expansion%20of%20personal%20data%20collection.%20This%20entire%20360%C2%B0%20profile%20setup%20to%20track%20us%20from%20birth%20to%20death%20has%20always%20been%20the%20foundation%20that%20Aadhaar%20was%20being%20built%20on%20and%20for.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20Bill%2C%20although%20it%20looks%20simple%20with%20mere%20changes%20to%20registration%20of%20births%20and%20deaths%2C%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20completely%20modify%20the%20relationship%20between%20an%20individual%20and%20the%20state.%20The%20Bill%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20pushed%20through%20the%20parliament%20this%20session%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20opposition.%20A%20vast%20majority%20of%20Indians%20might%20simply%20comply%20with%20this%20the%20same%20way%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20comply%20with%20Aadhaar.%20The%20present%20political%20conditions%20do%20not%20allow%20for%20any%20form%20of%20serious%20discussion%20on%20this%20Bill%20even%20outside%20the%20parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20much%20as%20one%20should%20be%20afraid%20of%20the%20surveillance%20state%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20capacity%20inside%20the%20state%20makes%20me%20wonder%20how%20long%20they%20will%20continue%20to%20push%20this%20without%20no%20opposition%20from%20the%20population.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%20is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689577698000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17123642%2FUntitled-design-23-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fregistration-of-births-deaths-aadhaar-voter-id%22%2C%22summary%22