f%20c%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehief%20managing%20director%2C%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3ECMD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chandrayaan-3%20was%20built%20with%20a%20budget%20of%20around%20Rs%20600%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689576083000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17120524%2Fimage-1124.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fengineers-who-built-chandrayaan-3-launch-pad-werent-paid-salaries-for-over-a-year-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20the%20issue%20of%20unpaid%20salaries%2C%20the%20firm%20delivered%20the%20mobile%20launching%20pad%20and%20other%20crucial%20and%20complex%20equipment%20ahead%20of%20schedule%20in%20December%202022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fengineers-who-built-chandrayaan-3-launch-pad-werent-paid-salaries-for-over-a-year-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20Reasons%20Why%20This%20Monsoon%20Crippled%20Delhi%20--%20And%20It's%20Not%20Just%20Rain%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20days%2C%20vast%20stretches%20of%20Delhi%20have%20been%20inundated%20due%20to%20the%20Yamuna%20river%20reaching%20its%20highest%20water%20level%20in%2045%20years%2C%20triggered%20by%20uncommonly%20heavy%20rainfall%2C%20some%20of%20which%20came%20from%20the%20neighboring%20state%20of%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flooding%20has%20displaced%20residents%2C%20submerged%20historical%20sites%20and%20roadways%2C%20claiming%20at%20least%20three%20lives.%20Officials%20and%20relief%20workers%20have%20been%20working%20to%20open%20jammed%20floodgates%20and%20repair%20broken%20drain%20regulators%20to%20control%20the%20water%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%205%20reasons%20why%20the%20monsoon%20crippled%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaryana%20floodgates%20open%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20water%20from%20the%20Hathnikund%20barrage%20in%20Haryana%20is%20being%20blamed%20as%20one%20of%20the%20factors%20that%20contributed%20to%20the%20waterlogging%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hathnikund%20barrage%20is%20situated%20on%20the%20border%20between%20Yamuna%20Nagar%20district%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Saharanpur%20district%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20barrage%20is%20managed%20by%20the%20Haryana%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20barrage%20was%20filled%20to%20capacity%20after%20receiving%20a%20large%20influx%20of%20water%20from%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20had%20recently%20experienced%20heavy%20rainfall.%20Typically%2C%20it%20releases%20352%20cusecs%20of%20water%20per%20hour.%20However%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20water%20released%20increases%20when%20there%20is%20heavy%20rainfall%20in%20the%20catchment%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22dlr1g8s%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fdlr1g8s_delhi-flood-pti_625x300_13_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20water%20level%20in%20the%20Yamuna%20river%20rose%20after%20the%20recent%20rains%2C%20causing%20the%20discharge%20from%20the%20barrage%20to%20spike.%20On%20July%209%2C%20at%204%20pm%2C%20111%2C060%20cusecs%20of%20water%20was%20released%20from%20the%20barrage.%20This%20is%20considered%20a%20%26quot%3Bflood%20situation%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20the%20release%20of%20more%20than%201%20lakh%20cusecs%20of%20water%20is%20considered%20a%20flood.%20The%20water%20release%20continued%20to%20rise%2C%20and%20on%20July%2011%2C%20at%20around%2011%20am%2C%203%2C59%2C769%20cusecs%20of%20water%20was%20released%20from%20the%20barrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20to%20the%20floodwaters%20entering%20several%20parts%20of%20Delhi%2C%20submerging%20entire%20localities%20and%20triggering%20a%20blame%20game%20between%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnprecedented%20rainfall%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETorrential%20rains%20lashed%20North%20India%20last%20week%2C%20causing%20widespread%20flooding%2C%20landslides%2C%20and%20other%20rain-related%20incidents.%20The%20weather%20office%20attributed%20the%20unprecedented%20rainfall%20to%20the%20confluence%20of%20a%20western%20disturbance%20and%20monsoonal%20winds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22huhj97a8%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fhuhj97a8_delhi-flood-ndtv_625x300_13_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heavy%20rain%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20Yamuna%20breaching%20its%20danger%20level%20by%20about%203%20metres%2C%20led%20to%20several%20localities%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20being%20flooded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeavy%20rain%20pounded%20Delhi%20again%20yesterday%20as%20the%20city%20continued%20to%20battle%20the%20severe%20flooding.%20The%20incessant%20downpour%20has%20exacerbated%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20authorities%20as%20it%20is%20taking%20more%20time%20to%20drain%20the%20floodwaters%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlocked%20regulators%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20claimed%20that%20the%20breaching%20of%20the%20Indraprastha%20water%20regulator%20was%20one%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20why%20Delhi%20experienced%20flooding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20regulator%20is%20a%20low-head%20dam%20or%20weir%20that%20controls%20the%20flow%20of%20floodwater%20back%20to%20the%20main%20channel%20from%20floodplains%20and%20diversion%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20regulator%20on%20drain%20number%2012%2C%20which%20carries%20water%20from%20central%20Delhi%20to%20the%20Yamuna%2C%20broke%20down%20Thursday%20evening%20around%207%20pm.%20This%20caused%20a%20backflow%20of%20water%20into%20the%20drain%2C%20which%20led%20to%20flooding%20in%20the%20ITO%20and%20surrounding%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEncroachments%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20attributed%20another%20reason%20for%20the%20severe%20flooding%20to%20the%20encroachment%20of%20the%20Yamuna%20floodplains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20noticed%20that%20the%20water%20released%20from%20the%20Hathnikund%20Barrage%20took%20less%20time%20to%20reach%20Delhi%20compared%20to%20previous%20years.%20The%20main%20reason%20could%20be%20encroachment%20and%20siltation.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20water%20would%20have%20had%20more%20space%20to%20flow.%20Now%2C%20it%20passes%20through%20a%20constricted%20cross-section%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20official%20at%20the%20Central%20Water%20Commission%20(CWC)%20said%20as%20quoted%20by%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EToo%20much%2C%20too%20soon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20leader%20Aatishi%20Singh%20have%20said%20recently%20that%20Delhi%20received%2020%25%20of%20the%20entire%20season's%20rain%20in%2024%20hours.%20Delhi%2C%20a%20city%20that%20historically%20does%20not%20receive%20rainfall%20of%20this%20magnitude%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%2C%20is%20not%20designed%20to%20handle%20floodwaters%20of%20this%20magnitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20master%20plan%20for%20Delhi%20after%20Independence%2C%20which%20was%20drawn%20up%20in%20the%201960s%2C%20had%20a%20major%20flaw.%20This%20flaw%20has%20only%20gotten%20worse%20over%20time%2C%20and%20it%20has%20contributed%20to%20the%20current%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22taps1i98%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ftaps1i98_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_14_July_23.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fheight%3D400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelhi's%20first%20master%20plan%20after%20Independence%20was%20drawn%20up%20in%201962%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20made%20a%20%26quot%3Bmistake%26quot%3B%20by%20treating%20the%20flood-prone%20Yamuna%20region%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bempty%20lot%26quot%3B%2C%20AK%20Jain%2C%20the%20former%20Commissioner%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Development%20Authority%20(DDA)%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelhi%20has%20been%20built%20and%20rebuilt%20many%20times%20over%20the%20last%201%2C000%20years.%20There's%20a%20river%20on%20one%20side%20and%20a%20ridge%20on%20the%20other.%20Delhi%20has%20always%20been%20settled%20between%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchitect%20Edward%20Lutyens%20was%20aware%20that%20the%20Yamuna%20riverbanks%20were%20prone%20to%20flooding%20and%20malaria%20outbreaks%20when%20the%20British%20decided%20to%20make%20Delhi%20the%20capital.%20However%2C%20construction%20of%20the%20new%20capital%20proceeded%20anyway%2C%20as%20King%20George%20V%20had%20already%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city's%20drainage%20system%20was%20designed%20in%20the%201970s%20for%20a%20population%20of%2030-35%20lakh.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20now%20overburdened%20by%20the%20current%20population%20of%202%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689575700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fnddegua_delhi-flood-pti_625x300_16_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-rain-delhi-flood-5-reasons-why-this-monsoon-crippled-delhi-and-its-not-just-rain-4214058%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20days%2C%20vast%20stretches%20of%20Delhi%20have%20been%20inundated%20due%20to%20the%20Yamuna%20river%20reaching%20its%20highest%20water%20level%20in%2045%20years%2C%20triggered%20by%20uncommonly%20heavy%20rainfall%2C%20some%20of%20which%20came%20from%20the%20neighboring%20state%20of%20Haryana.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-rain-delhi-flo