panel%20is%20said%20to%20have%20a%20broader%20mandate%20to%20review%20the%20framework%20and%20results%20of%20all%20surveys%20conducted%20under%20the%20National%20Statistical%20Office%20(NSO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPronab%20Sen%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20chief%20statistician%20and%20the%20former%20Chairman%20of%20the%20National%20Statistical%20Commission%2C%20has%20been%20named%20the%20new%20chair%20of%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%2010%20official%20members%2C%20and%20four%20non-official%20members%20who%20are%20eminent%20academics.%20The%20panel%20can%20have%20up%20to%2016%20members%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SCES%20was%20also%20chaired%20by%20Sen.%20It%20had%2028%20members%2C%20including%2010%20non-official%20members%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20comes%20after%20the%20previous%20round%20of%20household%20surveys%20on%20consumption%20expenditure%20and%20employment%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Feconomy-policy%2Fgovt-scraps-nso-s-consumer-expenditure-survey-over-data-quality-119111501838_1.html%5C%22%3Ewas%20discarded%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20concerns%20about%20%E2%80%9Cdata%20quality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20was%20issued%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Statistics%20and%20Programme%20Implementation%20(MOSPI)%20on%20July%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fgdp-growth-2023-high-economy%5C%22%3EThree%20Notes%20of%20Caution%20as%20India%20Celebrates%20Its%20GDP%20Growth%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20will%20help%20finalise%20survey%20results%2C%20but%20the%20NSC%20will%20have%20the%20ultimate%20authority%20to%20approve%20the%20publication%20of%20those%20results%2C%20the%20daily%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20comes%20amid%20sharp%20criticism%20of%20the%20Indian%20statistical%20machinery%20by%20experts%20from%20inside%20and%20outside%20the%20gov