s%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Franchi%2Fjharkhand-man-looks-up-youtube-videos-to-treat-toothache-dies%2Farticleshow%2F101812988.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20deceased%20originally%20belonged%20to%20the%20Nawadih%20block%20of%20Bokaro%20district.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Franchi%2Fjharkhand-man-looks-up-youtube-videos-to-treat-toothache-dies%2Farticleshow%2F101812988.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tomatoes%3A%20The%20Modi%20Government%20Has%20Made%20a%20PR%20Stunt%20Out%20of%20a%20Real%20Issue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17092648%2F20619182486_1b93f9420d_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20less%20than%20a%20year%20remaining%20until%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20is%20facing%20a%20significant%20round%20red%20obstacle%20that%20is%20both%20financially%20burdensome%20and%20concerning%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cspan%3Etomatoes%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etomatoes%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0has%20skyrocketed%20to%20Rs%20250%20per%20kg%2C%20rendering%20them%20over%20200%25%20more%20expensive%20than%20petrol%20(Rs%2097%20per%20litre%20in%20Delhi).%20Reports%20indicate%20a%20staggering%20445%25%20inflation%20in%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etomato%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0prices%2C%20making%20them%20unaffordable%20for%20the%20average%20citizen.%C2%A0%3Cspan%3ETomatoes%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0have%20essentially%20become%20a%20precious%20commodity%20or%20red%20gold%2C%20forcing%20individuals%20to%20choose%20between%20buying%202%20litres%20of%20petrol%20or%201%20kg%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etomatoes%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etomatoes%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20In%20the%20past%20month%2C%20it%20has%20become%20increasingly%20difficult%20for%20the%20working%20class%20in%20India%20to%20afford%20vegetables.%20Peas%2C%20ginger%20and%20other%20summer%20vegetables%20like%20pumpkin%2C%20gourds%20(%3Cem%3Elauki%2C%20tori%2C%20karela%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20and%20okra%2C%20along%20with%20limes%2C%20have%20all%20experienced%20sharp%20hyperinflation.%20This%20dire%20situation%20has%20prompted%20an%20RBI%20study%20to%20warn%20that%20the%20surge%20in%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etomato%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0prices%20could%20disrupt%20the%20trajectory%20of%20inflation.%20Major%20retail%20chains%20like%20McDonald%E2%80%99s%20have%20even%20removed%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etomatoes%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0from%20their%20burgers%20and%20wraps.%20And%20vernacular%20media%20is%20filled%20with%20reports%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etomato%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0burglaries%20and%20heists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etomato%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0crisis%20was%20triggered%20by%20erratic%20weather%20patterns.%20India%20has%20been%20facing%20extreme%20weather%20events%20this%20year%2C%20including%20heavy%20rain%20and%20heatwaves%2C%20which%20disrupted%20wheat%20production%20in%20central%20and%20northern%20India%20during%20the%20Rabi%20season.%20Furthermore%2C%20cyclones%20and%20untimely%20rains%20have%20wreaked%20havoc%20on%20off-season%20production%20regions%20in%20North%20India%2C%20such%20as%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20damaging%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etomato%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0farms%20in%20the%20southern%20and%20coastal%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20Although%20some%20farmers%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20managed%20to%20fetch%20over%20Rs%20100%20per%20kg%20for%20their%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etomatoes%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20their%20success%20was%20short-lived%20due%20to%20heavy%20rains%20that%20not%20only%20destroyed%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etomato%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0crops%20but%20also%20severely%20damaged%20hilly%20roads%20and%20national%20highways%2C%20disrupting%20the%20supply%20chain%20in%20many%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20climate%20change%20certainly%20plays%20a%20significant%20role%2C%20India%20has%20been%20grappling%20with%20supply%20chain%20issues%20for%20its%20three%20staple%20vegetables%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cspan%3Etomatoes%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20potatoes%2C%20and%20onions%20%E2%80%93%20for%20quite%20some%20time.%20A%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20launched%20Operation%20Greens%20and%20a%20TOP%20(%3Cspan%3Etomato%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20onion%2C%20potato)%20programme%2C%20which%20offered%20freight%20and%20infrastructure%20subsidies.%20However%2C%20red%20tape%20has%20had%20its%20way%2C%20and%20the%20current%20crisis%20has%20not%20been%20addressed.%20Erratic%20weather%20has%20put%20the%20scheme%20to%20the%20test%2C%20and%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20falling%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fcyclone-el-nino-is-the-modi-government-facing-heavy-weather%5C%22%3ECyclone%2C%20El%20Ni%C3%B1o%20%E2%80%93%20Is%20the%20Modi%20Government%20Facing%20Heavy%20Weather%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20implementing%20real-time%20measures%2C%20the%20government%20is%20soliciting%20solutions%20from%20the%20public%20when%20the%20crisis%20has%20reached%20its%20peak%2C%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cspan%3ETomato%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Grand%20Challenge%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20looks%20more%20like%20a%20PR%20stunt%20than%20a%20sincere%20effort%20to%20address%20the%20issue.%20This%20approach%20is%20disheartening%2C%20considering%20that%20just%20last%20season%2C%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etomato%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0farmers%20protested%20against%20plummeting%20prices%20by%20dumping%20truckloads%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etomatoes%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0onto%20the%20streets.%20Many%20farmers%20got%20Rs%201-2%20per%20kg%20for%20their%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etomato%3C%2Fspan%3E%20harvests%2C%20and%20onion%20prices%20were%20equally%20dismal.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20several%20farmers%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%20demanding%20government%20intervention%20to%20counter%20predatory%20market%20forces%20that%20intentionally%20suppressed%20%3Cspan%3Etomato%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0and%20onion%20prices.%20Unfortunately%2C%20there%20was%20no%20government%20programme%20or%20scheme%20in%20place%20to%20assist%20these%20struggling%20farmers%20in%20north%20and%20south%20India%2C%20resulting%20in%20massive%20wastage%20of%20vegetables%20as%20farmers%20had%20to%20bear%20the%20cost%20of%20selling%20their%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20remember%20that%2080%20crore%20Indians%20rely%20on%20the%20government%20for%20their%20food%20rations%2C%20but%20concrete%20plans%20to%20prevent%20harvest%20losses%20are%20conspicuously%20absent.%20NAFED%20and%20other%20agencies%20stood%20by%20as%20farmers%20were%20forced%20to%20destroy%20their%20vegetable%20harvests%2C%20while%20urban%20populations%20remained%20apathetic%20due%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20repeated%20assurances%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20is%20well%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20food%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etomato%3C%2Fspan%3E%20shortage%20is%20a%20failure%20of%20administration%20and%20agriculture.%20Had%20the%C2%A0%3Cspan%3ETomato%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Grand%20Challenge%20actively%20involved%20farmers%20as%20stakeholders%2C%20perhaps%20Indians%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20endure%20exorbitant%20prices%20for%20vegetables%20and%20%3Cspan%3Etomatoes%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20There%20is%20an%20urgent%20need%20to%20establish%20cold%20storage%20facilities%20at%20the%20village%20level%2C%20promote%20direct%20market%20links%20and%20introduce%20special%20Minimum%20Support%20Prices%20(MSP)%20for%20TOP%20vegetables%2C%20along%20with%20government%20procurement%20and%20growing%20quotas%20for%20farmers.%20Without%20such%20measures%2C%20India%20will%20struggle%20to%20emerge%20from%20this%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndra%20Shekhar%20Singh%20tweets%20at%20%40Indrassingh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20ne