ly%20assault%20her'.%20This%20is%20stated%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20filed%20by%20the%20police.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22S%20AHMED%20ALI%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bangladesh%3A%20Four%20killed%20as%20waterbus%20capsizes%20in%20Buriganga%20River%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689557501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101809258%2Cimgsize-54514.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladesh-four-killed-as-waterbus-capsizes-in-buriganga-river-many-missing%2Farticleshow%2F101809062.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F101809062.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladesh-four-killed-as-waterbus-capsizes-in-buriganga-river-many-missing%2Farticleshow%2F101809062.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladesh-four-killed-as-waterbus-capsizes-in-buriganga-river-many-missing%2Famp_articleshow%2F101809062.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladesh-four-killed-as-waterbus-capsizes-in-buriganga-river-many-missing%2Famp_articleshow%2F101809062.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20Will%20Strip%20the%20Marginalised%20of%20Their%20Constitutional%20Protections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F04165732%2FUntitled-design-2021-08-04T165720.758.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20as%20an%20agenda%20for%20legislation%20has%20surfaced%20again%20in%20the%20national%20discourse.%20The%20underlying%20idea%20driving%20this%20agenda%20is%20premised%20on%20the%20cause%20of%20gender%20equality%2C%20an%20important%20issue%20of%20concern%20that%20needs%20attention.%20The%20idea%20of%20equality%20generally%20is%20embodied%20in%20the%20concept%20of%20citizenship.%20However%2C%20the%20drive%20to%20equality%20has%20two%20dimensions.%20One%20refers%20to%20equality%20before%20the%20law%20or%20equal%20treatment%20to%20all%20before%20the%20law.%20Such%20a%20notion%20of%20equality%20does%20not%20necessarily%20lead%20to%20equality%20of%20opportunity%2C%20given%20the%20inequality%20inherent%20in%20the%20societal%20structure.%20After%20all%2C%20individuals%20with%20the%20status%20of%20citizenship%20are%20not%20outside%20of%20the%20communities%20%E2%80%93%20be%20they%20linguistic%2C%20religious%2C%20social%20or%20cultural.%20India%20epitomises%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20not%20a%20homogenous%20society%20with%20everyone%20speaking%20the%20same%20language%20and%20practising%20the%20same%20religion%2C%20traditions%20and%20customs%2C%20as%20is%20the%20case%20of%20many%20European%20countries.%20Rather%2C%20the%20opposite%20is%20true%2C%20leading%20to%20differences%20among%20its%20people%20concerning%20their%20personal%20life.%20Over%20and%20above%2C%20the%20communities%20so%20located%20are%20marked%20off%20by%20certain%20structures%20of%20inequality%20in%20the%20sphere%20of%20economy%2C%20polity%20and%20demography%2C%20with%20implications%20for%20unequal%20relations%20among%20individuals.%20While%20some%20communities%20stand%20privileged%2C%20others%20suffer%20disadvantages%20along%20one%20or%20more%20such%20parameters.%20Of%20the%20disadvantaged%20along%20community%20lines%2C%20language%2C%20religion%2C%20caste%20and%20tribe%20have%20generally%20been%20identified%20as%20the%20key%20criterion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20protection%20exists%20%E2%80%93%20and%20where%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20framers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20recognised%20the%20diversity%20and%20its%20intricate%20interface%20with%20varied%20dimensions%20of%20inequality.%20They%20were%20acutely%20aware%20that%20societies%20marked%20by%20diversity%20(linguistic%20and%20religious)%20are%20hardly%20on%20the%20same%20plane%20either%20in%20demographic%20terms%20or%20others%20such%20as%20development%20or%20a%20combination%20of%20both.%20They%20recognised%20that%20equality%20before%20law%20does%20not%20necessarily%20guarantee%20the%20equality%20of%20a%20level%20playing%20field.%20It%20is%20with%20this%20end%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20laid%20down%20protective%20provisions%20for%20certain%20groups%20and%20communities%20alongside%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20to%20freedom%2C%20equality%20and%20justice%20for%20every%20citizen%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20most%20talked%20about%20of%20such%20protective%20provisions%20has%20been%20the%20representation%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20through%20reservation%20in%20state%20employment%2C%20state-run%20higher%20educational%20institutions%20and%20political%20institutions%20such%20as%20the%20parliament%2C%20state%20legislature%20and%20even%20local%20self-governing%20institutions%20following%20the%2073rd%20and%2074th%20amendments%20in%201992.%20Such%20protective%20provisions%20have%20been%20positive%20steps%20toward%20the%20realisation%20of%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%2C%20however%2C%20protective%20provisions%20of%20other%20kinds%20which%20aim%20at%20safeguarding%20the%20identity%20and%20interests%20of%20religiously%2C%20linguistically%20and%20culturally%20disadvantaged%20groups%20that%20emanate%20from%20their%20being%20a%20numerical%20minority.%20This%20is%20best%20illustrated%20in%20provisions%20under%20Articles%2029(1)%20and%2030(1)%20meant%20for%20minorities%20and%20Articles%20244(1)%20and%20244(2)%20providing%20for%20the%205th%20and%206th%20schedules%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Articles%20371A%20and%20371G%20for%20Nagaland%20and%20Mizoram%2C%20respectively.%20In%20the%20protection%20of%20such%20provisions%2C%20however%2C%20the%20state%20has%20hardly%20provided%20or%20taken%20any%20concrete%20positive%20measures%20(excepting%20areas%20under%20the%206th%20schedule%20and%20with%20special%20constitutional%20status)%20to%20secure%20and%20safeguard%20their%20identity%20and%20interest%20%E2%80%93%20be%20it%20language%2C%20religion%20and%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20tribes%2C%20even%20land%20and%20forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Narendra%20Modi%20Knows%20an%20Actual%20UCC%20Will%20Be%20an%20Electoral%20Disaster%20for%20Him%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-knows-an-actual-ucc-will-be-an-electoral-disaster-for-him%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20Knows%20an%20Actual%20UCC%20Will%20Be%20an%20Electoral%20Disaster%20for%20Him%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20tribes%20have%20their%20language%20but%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20positive%20measures%20to%20protect%20and%20promote%20their%20language%20via%20school%20curriculum%20or%20other%20related%20measures%2C%20many%20tribal%20languages%20have%20become%20extinct%2C%20and%20many%20are%20already%20in%20the%20process.%20And%20so%20has%20been%20the%20case%20with%20tribal%20indigenous%2Ftraditional%20religions.%20Rather%20than%20recognising%20their%20distinct%20religious%20identity%2C%20these%20beliefs%20are%20being%20erased%20through%20the%20state%20administrative%20practice%20of%20co-option%20into%20the%20Hindu%20religious%20identity.%20The%20assertion%20for%20recognition%20of%20their%20distinct%20religious%20identity%20and%20their%20separate%20enumeration%20in%20the%20census%20today%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20India%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20process%20of%20reclaiming%20the%20above%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20these%20have%20been%20the%20result%20of%20the%20uniformisation%20of%20laws%2C%20policies%20and%20practices%20initiated%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20either%20by%20the%20Central%20or%20state%20governments.%20The%20violation%20of%20the%20provision%20inherent%20in%20the%205th%20schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20is%20the%20best%20example.%20Article%205(1)%20states%20that%20notwithstanding%20anything%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20governor%20may%20by%20public%20notification%20direct%20that%20any%20particular%20Act%20of%20the%20parliament%20or%20the%20state%20legislature%20shall%20not%20apply%20to%20a%20scheduled%20area%20or%20any%20part%20thereof%20in%20the%20state%20or%20shall%20apply%20subject%20to%20such%20exceptions%20and%20modifications%20as%20he%20may%20specify%20in%20the%20notification%20or%20any%20direction%20given%20under%20this%20sub-paragraph%20may%20be%20given%20to%20have%20retrospective%20effect.%20Yet%20all%20through%20post-independence%20India%2C%20governors%20never%20applied%20this%20power%20conferred%20on%20them%20to%20secure%20tribal%20interest%20and%20welfare.%20Rather%2C%20every%20law%20passed%20by%20the%20parliament%20and%20the%20state%20legislature%20was%20applied%20in%20scheduled%20areas%20with%20far-reaching%20consequences%20on%20their%20land%2C%20forest%20and%20livelihood%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20poorest%20social%20development%20indicators%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scenario%20in%206th%20schedule%20areas%20and%20states%20with%20special%20constitutional%20status%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Articles%20371A%20and%20371G%20is%20quite%20the%20opposite%20in%20all%20respects%20such%20as%20land%2C%20forest%2C%20language%2C%20customs%20and%20traditions%2C%20as%20the%20Constitution%20has%20given%20these%20areas%20a%20built-in%20institutional%20structure%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20Autonomous%20District%20Councils%20under%20the%206th%20schedule%20and%20states%20with%20special%20constitutional%20status%20to%20safeguard%20and%20promote%20their%20interests%20and%20identity.%20Further%2C%20unlike%20in%20the%205th%20schedule%20areas%20where%20the%20applicability%20of%20laws%20passed%20by%20parliament%20and%20state%20legislatures%20was%20vested%20in%20the%20office%20of%20the%20governor%20and%20his%20discretion%20which%20has%20hardly%20been%20used%2C%20the%20parliament-%20and%20state-enacted%20legislature%20concerned%20with%20subjects%20under%20the%206th%20schedule%20provision%20were%20not%20applicable%20in%20the%206th%20schedule%20areas.%20And%20so%20has%20been%20the%20case%20with%20parliament-enacted%20legislature%20on%20issues%20concerning%20social%2C%20religious%20and%20cultural%20practices%20in%20states%20with%20special%20constitutional%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUCC%20is%20an%20attack%20on%20constitutional%20provisions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20of%20a%20UCC%20is%20a%20brazen%20attack%20on%20the%20protective%20provisions%20inherent%20in%20the%20Constitution%20for%20religious%20minorities%20and%20cultural%20groups%20such%20as%20tribes.%20Moreover%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20being%20linguistic%20minorities%2C%20tribes%20also%20form%20religious%20minorities%2C%20both%20as%20Christians%20and%20practitioners%20of%20traditional%2Findigenous%20religions.%20Furthermore%2C%20tribal%20customary%20law%2C%20the%20font%20of%20personal%20law%20for%20tribal%20communities%2C%20has%20no%20religious%20moorings.%20For%20example%2C%20much%20of%20the%20personal%20life%20among%20tribal%20Christians%20is%20governed%20more%20by%20local%20tribal%20customs%20than%20religion%2C%20except%20for%20sacramental%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UCC%20poses%20challenges%20to%20such%20provisions%20inherent%20in%20the%20Constitution.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20comes%20in%20direct%20conflict%20with%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%206th%20schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20existing%20in%20Assam%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20Mizoram%20and%20Tripura.%20The%20same%20is%20the%20case%20for%20the%20states%20of%20Nagaland%20and%20Mizoram%20with%20special%20constitutional%20status%20of%20371A%20and%20371G%2C%20respectively.%20In%20both%20cases%2C%20the%20UCC%20violates%20constitutional%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22'UCC%20Is%20Merely%20an%20Attempt%20to%20Undo%20the%20Existing%20Muslim%20Law%2C%20Sixth%20Schedule%20Laws'%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fucc-is-merely-an-attempt-to-undo-the-existing-muslim-law-sixth-schedule-laws%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98UCC%20Is%20Merely%20an%20Attempt%20to%20Undo%20the%20Existing%20Muslim%20Law%2C%20Sixth%20Schedule%20Laws%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20the%205th%20schedule%2C%20it%20can%20prevail%20as%20the%20governors%2C%20as%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20have%20never%20used%20the%20power%20vested%20in%20them%20in%20the%20Constitution%20to%20secure%20and%20safeguard%20tribal%20interests%20and%20identity.%20The%20UCC%20may%20now%2C%20however%2C%20fall%20into%20legal%20entanglement%20while%20contending%20with%20the%20Provisions%20of%20the%20Panchayat%20Extension%20to%20Scheduled%20Areas%20(PESA)%20Act%201996.%20Provision%204(a)%20of%20the%20Act%20unequivocally%20states%20that%20any%20state%20Act%20introduced%20in%20PESA%20shall%20be%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20customary%20law%2C%20social%20and%20religious%20practices%20and%20traditional%20management%20practices%20of%20community%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20these%20protections%20are%20important%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20protective%20provisions%20have%20been%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20design%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20inequality%20not%20in%20the%20form%20of%20equality%20before%20the%20law%20but%20equal%20chances%20and%20conditions%20for%20the%20minority%20groups%20to%20practice%20and%20maintain%20their%20distinct%20social%2C%20religious%20and%20customary%20practices.%20This%20had%20taken%20the%20form%20of%20personal%20law%20in%20the%20case%20of%20religious%20minorities%20and%20the%20customary%20social%20and%20cultural%20practices%20in%20the%20case%20of%20tribes.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20the%20Constitution%20had%20made%20a%20space%20for%20legal%20pluralism%20as%20a%20step%20towards%20celebrating%20diversity%20and%20thereby%20facilitating%20the%20maintenance%20of%20their%20distinct%20identity.%20After%20all%2C%20in%20a%20society%20where%20they%20form%20a%20numerical%20minority%20plus%20economically%20and%20socially%20disadvantaged%2C%20these%20ensured%20protective%20provisions%20or%20mechanisms%20for%20minorities%20to%20have%20equal%20footing%20toward%20maintaining%20their%20identity%2C%20interest%2C%20and%20ways%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20absence%20of%20such%20provisions%2C%20it%20may%20have%20been%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20preserve%20and%20maintain%20their%20distinct%20identity%20as%20a%20minority%20in%20the%20country.%20Hence%20the%20Constitution%20equips%20them%20with%20constitutional%20protectionism.%20Yet%20while%20conferring%20citizenship%20rights%20in%20the%20form%20of%20equality%20before%20the%20law%2C%20such%20laws%20alone%20would%20have%20been%20unfair%20for%20vulnerable%20segments%20of%20society%20if%20special%20provisions%20were%20not%20made%20for%20them%20in%20the%20form%20of%20certain%20protective%20measures.%20%C2%A0Thus%2C%20the%20protective%20measures%20were%20a%20provision%20toward%20the%20realisation%20of%20what%20may%20be%20called%20%E2%80%9Cequality%20in%20conditions%20to%20ensure%20equality%20outcomes%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20such%20provisions%20pose%20the%20problem%20of%20citizenship%20in%20the%20sense%20of%20equal%20rights%20of%20the%20individuals%20within%20such%20groups%20and%20communities.%20This%20is%20most%20evident%20in%20gender%20inequality%2C%20which%20needs%20consideration%20and%20attention.%20However%2C%20the%20UCC%20is%20not%20the%20best%20of%20such%20means%20to%20achieve%20gender%20equality.%20The%20celebration%20of%20protective%20provisions%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Constitution%20is%20as%20important%20as%20the%20equality%20of%20individuals%20before%20the%20law%20as%20the%20UCC%20aims%20to%20achieve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20ethos%20and%20spirit%20of%20other%20protective%20provisions%20have%20not%20been%20adequately%20discussed%20and%20deliberated%20beyond%20the%20policy%20of%20reservation.%20Violating%20the%20protective%20laws%20by%20the%20general%20laws%20and%20policies%20in%20the%20name%20of%20equality%20or%20public%20good%2Fpublic%20purpose%20outwits%20the%20provision%20of%20equal%20conditions%20or%20start%20points%20provided%20in%20the%20Constitution%20for%20the%20marginalised%20and%20vulnerable.%20Often%20this%20is%20also%20discussed%20in%20the%20form%20of%20equality%20of%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founding%20fathers%20of%20the%20Constitution%20were%20acutely%20aware%20of%20this%20denial%20of%20equality%20in%20respect%20of%20religious%20and%20cultural%20minorities%20and%20hence%20made%20provisions%20for%20protective%20provisions%20in%20the%20Constitution.%20Such%20provisions%20in%20the%20constitution%20have%20been%20an%20aspect%20of%20celebration%20in%20the%20writings%20of%20legal%20luminaries%20and%20social%20scientists%20in%20the%201960s%20and%20%E2%80%9970s.%20However%2C%20the%20emergence%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20and%20gender%20issues%20that%20dominated%20the%20academic%20and%20civil%2C%20and%20political%20space%20since%20the%201980s%20led%20to%20much%20criticism%20of%20religious%20and%20cultural%20diversity%20on%20account%20of%20gender%20inequality%20overlooking%20the%20fact%20of%20other%20forms%20of%20marginality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGender%20inequality%20is%20indeed%20imperative%20and%20should%20be%20pursued%20but%20probably%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20carefully%20thought%20through%20and%20calibrated%20as%20an%20agenda%20for%20social%20inclusion%20and%20gender%20justice%20rather%20than%20as%20a%20one-size-fits-all%20approach%20by%20introducing%20the%20UCC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVirginius%20Xaxa%20is%20currently%20visiting%20professor%20at%20the%20Institute%20for%20Human%20Development%20(IHD)%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20Prior%20to%20joining%20IHD%2C%20he%20was%20Professor%20of%20Eminence%20and%20Bharat%20Ratna%20Lokapriya%20Gopinath%20Bordoloi%20Chair%20at%20Tezpur%20University%20(2016%E2%80%932018).%20He%20was%20also%20Professor%20and%20Deputy%20Director%20of%20the%20Tata%20Institute%20of%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20Guwahati%20Campus%20(2011%E2%80%932016).%20He%20taught%20Sociology%20at%20the%20Delhi%20School%20of%20Economics%2C%20University%20of%20Delhi%20(1990%E2%80%932011)%2C%20and%20North-Eastern%20Hill%20University%2C%20Shillong%20(1978%E2%80%931990).%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689557445000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F04165732%2FUntitled-design-2021-08-04T165720.758.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fa-uniform-civil-code-will-strip-the-marginalised-of-their-constitutional-protections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20announcement%20of%20a%20UCC%20is%20a%20brazen%20attack%20on%20the%20protective%20provisions%20inherent%20in%20the%20Constitution%20for%20religious%20minorities%20and%20cultural%20groups%20such%20as%20tribes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fa-uniform-civil-code-will-strip-the-marginalised-of-their-constitutional-protections%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22HBO%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Last%20Call%E2%80%99%20Director%20Almost%20Passed%20on%20the%20True%20Crime%20Docuseries%3A%20%E2%80%98My%20Biggest%20Concern%20Was%20Re-Victimizing%20the%20Queer%20Community%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689555600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Flast-call-when-a-serial-killer-stalked-queer-new-york_3-edited.jpg%3Fw%3D10