up%20in%20the%20next%20two%20months%20as%20the%20month-on-month%20rate%20of%20decline%20had%20reduced%20in%20June.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20smaller%20textile%20mills%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20were%20suspending%20production%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20orders%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20K.M.%20Subramanian%2C%20president%20of%20Tiruppur%20Exporters%20Association%2C%20said%20the%20smaller%20companies%20were%20the%20worst%20affected%20in%20the%20Tiruppur%20cluster.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFactors%20such%20as%20slowdown%20in%20the%20U.S.%20and%20EU%20and%20lack%20of%20cost%20competitiveness%20were%20affecting%20textile%20and%20clothing%20exports.%20The%20yarn%20that%20should%20be%20exported%20is%20coming%20into%20the%20domestic%20market.%20There%20is%20already%20excess%20capacity%20in%20the%20country.%20These%20were%20among%20the%20factors%20affecting%20the%20textile%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fbusiness%2Ftextile-exports-continue-to-decline-in-june-mills-suspend-work-on-tepid-demand%2Farticle67084560.ece%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20CITI%20chairman%20T.%20Rajkumar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERavi%20Sam%2C%20chairman%20of%20Southern%20India%20Mills%E2%80%99%20Association%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20a%20free%20trade%20agreement%20with%20the%20UK%20would%20grant%20immediate%20relief%20to%20the%20Indian%20textile%20industry.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20expensive%20because%20of%209%25%20to%2011%25%20duty%20in%20the%20UK%20market.%20If%20India%20gets%20duty-free%20access%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20steep%20jump%20in%20orders%20for%20garment%20and%20made-up%20exporters%20from%20their%20existing%20customers.%20This%20will%20revive%20demand%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajkumar%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fbusiness%2Ftextile-expor