7%2FScreen-Shot-2021-08-18-at-2.31.17-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20recent%20survey%20report%20suggests%20that%20nearly%20two%20out%20of%20three%20people%20in%20Gujarat%20are%20reluctant%20to%20express%20their%20political%20and%20social%20opinion%20online.%20This%20fear%2C%20the%20survey%20report%20prepared%20by%20NGO%20Common%20Cause%20and%20Lokniti%2C%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies%20(CSDS)%20suggests%2C%20is%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20legal%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20news%20report%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fthesundaystandard%2F2023%2Fjul%2F16%2Fin-gujarat-33-of-people-very-scared-of-legal-impact-of-political-views-online-2595282.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAHMEDABAD%253A%2520Nearly%2520two%2520out%2520of%2Cfor%2520the%2520Study%2520of%2520Developing%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20NGO%E2%80%99s%20report%20titled%20%E2%80%98Status%20of%20Policing%20in%20India%20Report%202023%E2%80%99%2C%20looked%20at%20the%20behaviour%20of%20internet%20users%20in%20Gujarat.%20The%20study%2C%20TNIE%20article%20says%2C%20shows%20that%2033%25%20of%20those%20surveyed%20were%20extremely%20scared%20about%20inciting%20legal%20action%20by%20expressing%20their%20political%20opinions%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20study%2C%20while%20most%20respondents%20backed%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20surveillance%20of%20mobile%20phones%20to%20curb%20political%20protests%2C%20many%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20their%20own%20capacity%20to%20openly%20express%20their%20social%20or%20political%20beliefs%20online%20for%20fear%20of%20legal%20repercussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20TNIE%2C%20Mahashweta%20Jani%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20coordinator%20of%20%E2%80%98Lokniti%E2%80%99%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20single%20party%20has%20ruled%20for%20a%20long%20time%20in%20a%20state%2C%20the%20overall%20fear%20of%20surveillance%20within%20the%20public%20is%20very%20natural%2C%20due%20to%20autocracy%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20people%20are%20afraid%20to%20express%20their%20political%20opinion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20has%20found%20that%20Gandhinagar%20has%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20CCTV%20cameras%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20part%20of%20the%20survey%2C%20participants%20were%20asked%20if%20they%20are%20afraid%20of%20legal%20action%20if%20their%20social%20media%20posts%20on%20a%20political%20or%20social%20topic%20offend%20certain%20groups.%20Most%20respondents%20said%20yes.%20In%20Gujarat%2C%2033%25%20of%20people%20stated%20they%20are%20very%20scared%20of%20legal%20punishment%20for%20sharing%20political%20or%20social%20opinions%20online.%20Other%2046%25%20said%20they%20are%20%E2%80%9Csomewhat%20scared%E2%80%9D.%20Around%209%20%25%20stated%20they%20are%20less%20scared%3B%20while%20only%208%25%20said%20they%20are%20not%20scared%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689506125000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F18143157%2FScreen-Shot-2021-08-18-at-2.31.17-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsurvey-finds-33-in-gujarat-are-scared-to-share-political-opinions-online%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20part%20of%20the%20survey%2C%20participants%20were%20asked%20if%20they%20are%20afraid%20of%20legal%20action%20if%20their%20social%20media%20posts%20on%20a%20political%20or%20social%20topic%20offend%20certain%20groups.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsurvey-finds-33-in-gujarat-are-scared-to-share-political-opinions-online%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Heat%20storm'%20stretches%20into%20southern%20Europe%2C%20health%20alerts%20issued%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689505871000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F