block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201378px)%20100vw%2C%201378px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmoms1-min-1689255976.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221378%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bengaluru%20mothers%20Anupama%20Harish%20and%20Charulatha%20R%20hosted%20a%20low-waste%20plastic-free%20wedding%20for%20their%20children%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmoms1-min-1689255976.jpeg%201378w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmoms1-min-1689255976-258x300.jpeg%20258w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmoms1-min-1689255976-500x581.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmoms1-min-1689255976-768x892.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmoms1-min-1689255976-1323x1536.jpeg%201323w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmoms1-min-1689255976-150x174.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323758%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnupama%20and%20Charulatha%20organised%20a%20low-waste%20wedding%20for%20their%20children.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlastic%20litter%20has%20always%20bothered%20me.%20We%20already%20compost%20at%20home%20and%20I%20have%20a%20terrace%20garden%20where%20I%20use%20it.%20Even%20the%20engagement%20ceremony%20we%20arranged%20did%20not%20have%20plastic%2C%20so%20we%20gladly%20took%20up%20the%20challenge%20of%20having%20a%20plastic-free%20wedding%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnupama%20also%20took%20responsibility%20for%20handling%20the%20waste%20and%20ensuring%20that%20the%20wedding%20was%20plastic%20free.%20She%20mentions%20that%20half%20of%20the%20efforts%20required%20to%20successfully%20execute%20such%20a%20wedding%20should%20be%20done%20during%20the%20planning%20stage%2C%20beginning%20with%20the%20invitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPlanning%20a%20plastic-free%20wedding%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fcutlery-min-1689256097.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Steel%20cutlery%20was%20rented%20for%20the%20wedding.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fcutlery-min-1689256097.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fcutlery-min-1689256097-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fcutlery-min-1689256097-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fcutlery-min-1689256097-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fcutlery-min-1689256097-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fcutlery-min-1689256097-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fcutlery-min-1689256097-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323761%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20mothers%20rented%20steel%20cutlery%20for%20the%20wedding.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20reduce%20waste%2C%20both%20the%20bride%20and%20groom%E2%80%99s%20side%20printed%20minimum%20invitation%20cards%2C%20which%20carried%20the%20words%3A%20%E2%80%98We%20are%20attempting%20a%20minimum%20waste%20wedding.%20We%20sincerely%20request%20you%20to%20avoid%20bouquets%20and%20gift%20wrappers%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20weddings%20are%20usually%20lavish%20and%20extravagant.%20If%20you%20visit%20any%20wedding%20venue%20after%20the%20festivities%20are%20over%2C%20you%20will%20find%20it%20strewn%20with%20plastic%20bottles%2C%20cups%2C%20and%20decoration%20items.%20As%20weddings%20get%20larger%2C%20so%20is%20the%20wastage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20major%20waste%20producers%20in%20a%20wedding%20is%20food.%20According%20to%20an%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3EGround%20Report%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAn%20average%20Indian%20wedding%20generates%20about%20200%E2%80%93300%20kg%20of%20food%20waste%20which%20amounts%20to%20almost%2020%25%20of%20the%20food%20going%20to%20waste.%20Cumulatively%2C%20it%20amounts%20to%20%2414%20billion%20worth%20of%20meals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20decided%20on%20a%20menu%20that%20would%20involve%20less%20cutlery%20and%20chose%20dishes%20accordingly.%20We%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20any%20plastic%20cups%20or%20water%20bottles.%20We%20rented%20steel%20cutlery%20from%20Adamya%20Chetana%2C%20a%20free%20cutlery%20bank.%20Food%20was%20served%20on%20banana%20leaves.%20We%20only%20used%20steel%20plates%20for%20the%20reception%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anupama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20would%20usually%20think%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291582%2Fplan-green-eco-friendly-indian-wedding-with-ebikes-cycles-in-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow-waste%20execution%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20only%20possible%20in%20small-scale%20weddings.%20But%20Anupama%20and%20Charulatha%20made%20sure%20the%20template%20worked%20for%20their%20big%20fat%20Indian%20wedding.%20They%20had%20more%20than%201%2C000%20guests%20for%20the%20reception%20and%20%3Cem%3Emuhurtam%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Yet%2C%20no%20plastic%20waste%20was%20generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201125px)%20100vw%2C%201125px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-13-at-16.02.02-1689256290.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Flowers%20and%20lights%20were%20used%20for%20the%20wedding%20decoration.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-13-at-16.02.02-1689256290.jpeg%201125w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-13-at-16.02.02-1689256290-300x211.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-13-at-16.02.02-1689256290-500x352.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-13-at-16.02.02-1689256290-768x541.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-13-at-16.02.02-1689256290-150x106.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323765%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22793%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFlowers%20and%20lights%20were%20used%20for%20the%20wedding%20decoration.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20that%20no%20waste%20from%20the%20wedding%20ends%20up%20in%20the%20landfill%2C%20Anupama%20roped%20in%20her%20%E2%80%98composting%20guru%E2%80%99%20Vasuki%20Iyengar%20to%20achieve%20this%20feat.%20A%20member%20of%20the%20Solid%20Waste%20Management%20Round%20Table%20(SWMRT)%20Bengaluru%2C%20Vasuki%20along%20with%20the%20six%20other%20members%20of%20the%20SWMRT%20team%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20handling%20all%20the%20waste%20from%20the%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20SWMRT%2C%20over%204%2C000%20meals%20were%20served%20during%20the%20wedding%2C%20spread%20over%20three%20days.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThis%20led%20to%20about%201%2C000%20kg%20of%20wet%20waste%2C%20which%20was%20turned%20into%20300%20kg%20of%20compost%20later%20on.%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fswmrt-1689256433.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20SWMRT%20team%20that%20handled%20the%20wedding%20waste%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fswmrt-1689256433.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fswmrt-1689256433-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fswmrt-1689256433-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fswmrt-1689256433-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fswmrt-1689256433-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fswmrt-1689256433-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323767%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20SWMRT%20team%20handled%20the%20waste%20collected%20during%20the%20wedding%20and%20composted%20it%20later.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLow-waste%20weddings%20are%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vasuki.%20%E2%80%9CBiodegradable%20waste%20is%20usually%20mixed%20with%20plastic%20waste%20and%20dumped%20in%20landfills.%20So%20our%20team%20was%20present%20at%20the%20venue%2C%20and%20we%20placed%20drums%20filled%20with%20cocopeat%20to%20collect%20the%20waste.%20We%20instructed%20the%20kitchen%2C%20catering%20and%20cleaning%20staff%20to%20segregate%20the%20waste%20and%20put%20the%20wet%20waste%20in%20the%20drums.%20The%20paper%20and%20flower%20waste%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20collection%20centre.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wet%20waste%20collected%20from%20the%20wedding%20was%20composted%20at%20the%20Swachagraha%20Kalika%20Kendra.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20by%20using%20steel%20cutlery%2C%2030%2C000%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F195354%2Fbengaluru-couple-eco-friendly-wedding-planning-tips-steel-cutlery-rent-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esingle-use%20disposables%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20avoided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUsing%2019-year-old%20butter%20paper%20for%20gifts%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpackaging-1689256526.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Butter%20paper%20used%20to%20wrap%20gifts%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpackaging-1689256526.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpackaging-1689256526-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpackaging-1689256526-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpackaging-1689256526-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpackaging-1689256526-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323769%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOld%20butter%20paper%20was%20used%20to%20wrap%20gifts.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20big%20aspect%20of%20Indian%20weddings%20is%20the%20gifts.%20While%20going%20through%20her%20attic%2C%20Anupama%20found%20a%20huge%20bundle%20of%20butter%20paper%20which%20she%20had%20stowed%20away%20after%20her%20son%E2%80%99s%20thread%20ceremony%20in%202004.%20She%20used%20that%20to%20pack%20the%20gifts%20for%20the%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20gave%20everyone%20naturally%20dyed%20blouse%20pieces.%20Even%20if%20one%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stitch%20it%2C%20they%E2%80%99ll%20definitely%20hand%20it%20over%20to%20someone%20else.%20I%20also%20used%20all%20the%20%3Cem%3Earishina%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ekumkuma%20(turmeric%20and%20vermillion%20powder)%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20I%20had%20at%20home%20and%20packed%20them%20in%20papers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anupama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20used%20only%20fresh%20flowers%20for%20decorations.%20Later%20on%2C%20the%20bride%E2%80%99s%20friends%20sent%20the%20flowers%20to%20a%20studio%20in%20Mumbai%20which%20used%20them%20as%20natural%20dyes%20and%20created%20clothes%20for%20the%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuf6roDg0sV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuf6roDg0sV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuf6roDg0sV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Vasuki%20Iy